NK079(dzu)003:1: // thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo'i phreng ba'i 'grel pa bzhugs //
NK079(dzu)003:2: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo'i phreng ba'i don bsdus pa'i 'grel pa /
NK079(dzu)003:3: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:4: theg pa chen po la don rnam pa gnyis te /
NK079(dzu)003:5: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:7: de la mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:8: mdo sde dag la sogs pa'i tshul gyis /
NK079(dzu)003:9: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa spyad pas bskal pa grangs med pa gsum gyi sa gnon pa ste /
NK079(dzu)003:10: yun ring po nas pha rol tu phyin pa bcu la sogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:11: bka' ba sna tshogs pa spyod pas grub ces 'byung /
NK079(dzu)003:12: rdo rje theg pa ni gsang sngags kyi sgo nas 'jug pa ste //
NK079(dzu)003:13: rdo rje lta bu rnam pa gsum gyi mthu rnyed nas /
NK079(dzu)003:15: de ni theg pa chen po'i yang chen po zhes bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:17: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i chos thams dkyil 'khor gsum du 'dus shing /
NK079(dzu)003:18: zhing dang spyod yul yongs su dag pas /
NK079(dzu)003:19: yon tan gyi khyad par gong na med de /
NK079(dzu)003:20: bcom ldan 'das kyi gsungs pa thams cad kyi nang na yang bkri ba'i don ma yin gyi /
NK079(dzu)003:21: nges pa'i don gtan la phab pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:22: rmad du byung ba'i sde las btus te bstan to //
NK079(dzu)003:23: de la 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa /
NK079(dzu)003:24: pad mo phreng ba'i don bsdus pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:25: de la 'phags pa ni nyan thos dag kyang 'jig
NK079(dzu)003:26: rten las 'phags mod kyi skabs 'dir de la mi
NK079(dzu)003:27: bya'o // theg pa chen po'i yang chen po /
NK079(dzu)003:28: nyan thos dang yun ring po nas 'grub pa las 'phags pa ste /
NK079(dzu)003:29: tshe 'di nyid la grub pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:30: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das chen po la bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:31: thabs kyi zhags pa zhes bya ba ni thabs ni snying rje chen po ste /
NK079(dzu)003:32: mtshams med pa lnga la sogs pa la rol cing /
NK079(dzu)003:33: phyin ci log la zhen pa'i sems can rnams sgrol ba'o //
NK079(dzu)003:34: zhags pa ni mi gtong ba ste /
NK079(dzu)003:35: 'khor ba nyid mnyam pa'i chos su mkhyen pas /
NK079(dzu)003:36: 'khor bar mi gtong bar sbyor ba la bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:37: 'di ni sbyor ba rnam gnyis zhes bya /
NK079(dzu)003:38: che mchog rnam gnyis zhes kyang 'byung //
NK079(dzu)003:39: pad mo zhes bya ba la /
NK079(dzu)003:40: pad+ma ni shes rab kyi rtags te /
NK079(dzu)003:41: chos thams cad la dpyod kyang /
NK079(dzu)003:45: sprul pa'i phreng ba rgyun ma chad pa la bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:46: dper na thabs dang shes rab zung 'brel bas //
NK079(dzu)003:47: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa mi gnas pa'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:48: don bsdus pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:50: tan tra sde bco brgyad la sogs pa las bsdus pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:51: de nas bcom ldan 'das dpal kun rigs rnam par snang mdzad la /
NK079(dzu)003:52: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' rig pa'i byin rlabs las byung ba'i mchod pas /
NK079(dzu)003:53: rgya yongs su ma chad pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK079(dzu)003:57: sgeg mo la sogs pa phyi nang gi mchod pa brgyad kyis mchod de /
NK079(dzu)003:58: lan gsum bskor ba byas nas /
NK079(dzu)003:59: so so rig pa 'dun pa'i phyag 'tshal nas //
NK079(dzu)003:62: zhes bya ba ni bcom ldan 'das dpal rnam par snang mdzad la /
NK079(dzu)003:63: rdo rje sems dpas don bsdus par gsol ba'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:64: rig pa'i byin gyis brlabs las byung ba'i mchod pa'i sprin chen pos mchod de /
NK079(dzu)003:65: 'og nas byung ba'i 'di skad gsol ba btab pa'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:66: bcom ldan 'das dus gsum du gshegs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis mkhyen pa /
NK079(dzu)003:67: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyi spyod yul /
NK079(dzu)003:68: nyan thos dang thun mong ma lags pa thabs gang gis rtogs pa de /
NK079(dzu)003:69: tshe 'di nyid la thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang
NK079(dzu)003:70: thob par 'gyur ba'i don brlabs te bshad du gsol
NK079(dzu)003:71: / zhes lan gsum du gsol ba btab bo //
NK079(dzu)003:72: zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:73: de skad gsol ba btab pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:74: ci yang mi gsungs pa 'dzum pa mdzad nas //
NK079(dzu)003:77: rdo rje sems dpa' don bsdu bar gsol ba gnang nas /
NK079(dzu)003:78: da ltar dang ma 'ongs pa'i sems can thams cad la phan pa'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:79: don bsdu bar gsol ba 'di yin no snyam nas dgyes te /
NK079(dzu)003:80: 'dzum pa mdzad nas 'og ma nas 'byung ba skad bka' stsal ces bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:81: sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /don 'di dang phyi nang gi chos thams cad 'dra ste /
NK079(dzu)003:83: bden pa gnyis la tshul 'di ltar rig par bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:87: rdo rje sems dpa' la bos pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:88: 'di'i don dang phyi nang gi chos thams cad 'dra ste /
NK079(dzu)003:90: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng gi don dang /
NK079(dzu)003:92: bcud kyi 'jig rten gyi chos thams cad 'dra'o zhes bya ba'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:95: snod bcud kyi 'jig rten gyi chos dang /
NK079(dzu)003:96: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+ma phreng gi don dang 'dra ste /
NK079(dzu)003:97: chos thams cad bden pa gnyis su 'dus pa'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:98: de la bden pa gnyis ni gang /
NK079(dzu)003:99: tshul ci ltar rtogs par bya zhe na /
NK079(dzu)003:100: bden pa gnyis la tshul 'di ltar rigs par bya zhes smos te /
NK079(dzu)003:101: bden pa gnyis ni don dam pa'i bden pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:103: de yang nyan thos kyi ltar ma yin gyis /
NK079(dzu)003:104: chos thams cad mtshan ma med pa las byung bas /
NK079(dzu)003:106: sgyu ma tsam du snang bas /
NK079(dzu)003:107: kun rdzob kyi 'bras bur rig par bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:109: bden gnyis rgyu dang 'bras bu'i tshul //
NK079(dzu)003:110: de bzhin nyid la gnas bcas nas //
NK079(dzu)003:111: phyi nang snod bcud rnam par dag /byed dpyod thams cad tshogs gnyis 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)003:114: chen po gcig gi nang na yang lnga yod de /
NK079(dzu)003:116: chen po lnga yang ma grub ste /
NK079(dzu)003:118: nang bcud kyi 'jig rten lta bu yang /
NK079(dzu)003:119: sems dang sems las byung ba'i chos snga ma ni 'das /
NK079(dzu)003:121: da lta ni mi gnas pas rang bzhin med do //
NK079(dzu)003:123: don dam pa'i bden pa ste rgyu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:124: de las so so'i rtsal sgyu ma tsam du yod pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:125: kun rdzob kyi bden pa ste 'bras bu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:126: chos de dag gi de bzhin nyid ni don dam pa ste /
NK079(dzu)003:127: rgyu la mi gnas pa'i tshul gyis gnas nas /
NK079(dzu)003:128: phyi nang gi snod bcud kyi 'jig rten 'bras bu'i
NK079(dzu)003:129: chos la ji ltar dpyad kyang sgrib pa rnam gnyis
NK079(dzu)003:131: de ltar chos thams cad la dpyad kyang /
NK079(dzu)003:133: bag chags su mi 'gyur pa ni ye shes kyi tshogs so //
NK079(dzu)003:134: bdag dang 'phags pa thams cad mnyam pa'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:135: spyod pa ni bsod nams kyi tshogs su 'gyur zhes bya ba'i don no //
NK079(dzu)003:136: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs ni /
NK079(dzu)003:137: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu dpyad pas rdzogs zhes 'byung na /
NK079(dzu)003:138: de dag rdzogs sam zhe na /
NK079(dzu)003:140: pha rol phyin bcu rdzogs pa ste //
NK079(dzu)003:141: sa bcu rim gyi bkod pa la //
NK079(dzu)003:142: mnyam nyid rig pa'i rdo rje yis //
NK079(dzu)003:143: sa rnams mnyam pa nyid du sbyor //
NK079(dzu)003:146: chos thams cad la dpyod pa ni //
NK079(dzu)003:147: sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa'i 'bras bu dang bcas pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:148: nyon mongs pa rnam par byang ba mi zhan par rig nas /
NK079(dzu)003:149: bdag dang 'phags pa thams cad so so ma yin tha mi dad par rtogs pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:150: tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:151: 'di lta bu'i chos la bzod pa'am /
NK079(dzu)003:152: 'khrul par 'gyur kyang sgrib pa mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK079(dzu)003:153: mtshan dang dpe byad 'og nas 'byung ba ltar rig pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:154: bzod pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:155: spyod lam rnam bzhir gnyid log kyang /
NK079(dzu)003:156: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs su rig pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:157: 'bad pa med pa'i brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:158: dbang po lnga ni rigs lnga /
NK079(dzu)003:159: yul lnga ni yum lnga'i rig nas /
NK079(dzu)003:161: chos dbyings las mi 'gyur bar rig cing /
NK079(dzu)003:162: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK079(dzu)003:163: chos thams cad la thogs pa med par 'jug pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:164: bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:167: so so ma yin par rig pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:168: nyan thos las khyad par che bas //
NK079(dzu)003:169: shes pa ni nang na khyad par che'am /
NK079(dzu)003:171: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:172: kun nas nyon mongs pa'i chos thams cad /
NK079(dzu)003:173: rnam par byang ba'i chos su rig cing /
NK079(dzu)003:174: 'phags pa thams cad chad mnyes pas /
NK079(dzu)003:175: bdag dang gzhan gyi don du 'gyur zhing grol ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:176: thabs kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:177: bdag dang 'phags pa thams cad so so ma yin pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:178: zhing dang spyod yul thams cad yongs su dag par rig pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:179: smon lam kyi pha rol du phyin pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:180: 'khor ba dang kun nas nyon mongs pa las /
NK079(dzu)003:182: rnam par byang ba gud na med par rig ste /
NK079(dzu)003:183: 'khor ba dang kun nas nyon mongs pa gnod pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:184: stobs kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:185: gang zag la bdag med par rtogs pas /
NK079(dzu)003:186: bag chags la sogs pa'i gnas med cing chos la bdag med pas /
NK079(dzu)003:187: bag chags rang rang gi ngo bo yang med par rig cing /
NK079(dzu)003:188: de ltar rig pa'i ye shes su dus thams cad du 'gyur ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:189: ye shes kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:191: sa dang po nas bcu pa'i bar du ste /
NK079(dzu)003:192: nyan thos kyi ltar rim gyis bsgrod pa ni ma yin gyi /
NK079(dzu)003:193: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes rdo rjes /
NK079(dzu)003:194: mnyam pa nyid du sbyor bas /
NK079(dzu)003:195: sa bcu yang tshe 'di nyid la skad cig gis rdzogs par byed do //
NK079(dzu)003:197: sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /zhes bya ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:198: kun nas nyon mongs pa'i chos dang /
NK079(dzu)003:200: mtshan nyid gcig tu ston pa las /
NK079(dzu)003:201: the tshom za bar dogs nas /
NK079(dzu)003:203: rdo rje lta bu'i ye shes kyis //
NK079(dzu)003:204: chos kun sgyu mar rig pa'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)003:205: dngos dang dngos med bag chags bsregs //
NK079(dzu)003:206: yang na ye shes me zhes bya //
NK079(dzu)003:208: stong pa nyid kyis ye shes kyis //
NK079(dzu)003:209: chos thams cad sgyu mar rig pa'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:210: dngos po rtag par lta ba dang /
NK079(dzu)003:211: stong pa chad par lta ba la sogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:212: las legs nyes gnyis kyi bag chags bsregs pa'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:213: ye shes kyi me zhes bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:215: dgu dang 'bras bu rnam smin ni //
NK079(dzu)003:216: med min rgyu 'bras mthun par grub //
NK079(dzu)003:217: de bzhin mnyam nyid ye shes kyis //
NK079(dzu)003:218: rig pa tshogs su 'gyur bas so //
NK079(dzu)003:220: las dge sdig gi 'bras bu ni //
NK079(dzu)003:221: dper na mun pa'i nang du sgron me byung na /
NK079(dzu)003:222: mun pa'i bsam pas sgron ma 'ong bas mun pa bros so snyam du yang mi sems kyi /
NK079(dzu)003:224: mun pa bsal lo snyam du mi sems mod kyi /
NK079(dzu)003:226: mun pa chos nyid kyis 'gro ba dang 'dra bar /
NK079(dzu)003:227: las dge sdig kyang mtho ris dang /
NK079(dzu)003:228: ngan song bsgrub bo snyam yang mi sems /
NK079(dzu)003:229: mtho ris ngan song gis kyang /
NK079(dzu)003:230: dge sdig bsgrub bo snyam mi sems med kyi /
NK079(dzu)003:231: sems kyi khyad par gyi de ltar grub bo //
NK079(dzu)003:232: de bzhin du chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rig pas kyang /
NK079(dzu)003:233: sangs rgyas su bsgrub bo snyam du mi sems kyi /
NK079(dzu)003:234: chos kyis grub ces bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:235: de la yang mnyam pa nyid la yang rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK079(dzu)003:236: phyi'i yul chen po lnga ste /
NK079(dzu)003:237: de bzhin gshegs pa sngar mnyam pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:238: nang gi sems ye shes mnyam pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:240: lha mo'i tshul du mnyam pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:241: don dam par skye 'gags med pa tshul du mnyam pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:242: de lta bu chos mnyam pa nyid kyi rig pa dang mi ldan na /
NK079(dzu)003:243: mi dge bcu'i las kyi 'bras bu ni /
NK079(dzu)003:244: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal du lhung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:245: dge ba bcus ni 'dod khams kyi lha dang mir grub bo //
NK079(dzu)003:246: mi g.yo bas ni gzugs dang gzugs med pa'i khams su skyes te /
NK079(dzu)003:247: de dag ni rnam par smin pa zad nas //
NK079(dzu)003:249: de bas na dpal mchog dang po las /
NK079(dzu)003:250: sems dpa' chen po rang gi rig pa'i ye shes
NK079(dzu)003:251: kyis sems can thams cad mnyam pa nyid rtog pa
NK079(dzu)003:252: med na / sangs rgyas kyi sa la spyi bo nas lag gis drangs te bzhag na yang /
NK079(dzu)003:253: sems can dmyal ba'i gnas su mthong ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:256: sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag par mthong ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:258: dper na lha'i bu dri ma med pa'i 'od kyang /
NK079(dzu)003:259: ngan song sbyong ba'i dkyil 'khor byas pas /
NK079(dzu)003:260: ngan song las mtho ris su thar gyi /
NK079(dzu)003:261: rang rig pa'i ye shes med pas sangs rgyas ma grub bo zhes bshad do //
NK079(dzu)003:262: de bas chos thams cad la mnyam pa nyid du rig nas /
NK079(dzu)003:263: dge sdig gi chos thams cad 'dra ste /
NK079(dzu)003:264: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs su 'gyur zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:265: mnyam pa nyid kyi don gsal bar rig pa med pa rnams kyis ni /
NK079(dzu)003:266: dge bcu la goms par bya ba rigs so //
NK079(dzu)003:267: mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa rnams kyis kyang //
NK079(dzu)003:268: dge ba bcu la gtsor len pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:269: de nyid mnyam par mi rung ste //
NK079(dzu)003:270: nyan thos kyi sa yin no //
NK079(dzu)003:271: theg pa chen po'i chos gnyis ka /sangs rgyas kyi snod rim pa dang sbyar te //
NK079(dzu)003:272: sems can gyi don du 'byung bar gsungs pa 'dra bas /
NK079(dzu)003:273: nyan thos kyi chos la lhag par sems 'byung zhing spang bar mi rung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:274: rang gi shes rab rtul bas /
NK079(dzu)003:275: chos mnyam pa nyid ma rtogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK079(dzu)003:276: chos mnyam pa nyid sems dbyung bar mi bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:277: rnam pa gcig tu na sems can dmyal ba'i chos kyang mi bkol ces 'byung na /
NK079(dzu)003:278: nyan thos lta ci smos te /
NK079(dzu)003:279: thams cad mnyam par spyod de /
NK079(dzu)003:280: tshe 'di nyid la thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang thob ces gsungs pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:281: lam gyi nang na nye lam bde rdzogs pa //
NK079(dzu)003:282: thabs kyi nang na ma nor dam pa ste //
NK079(dzu)003:283: bsgrub na tshe 'dir sangs rgyas che ba yang //
NK079(dzu)003:284: blang dor med pas sku rdo rje thob ces gsungs te /
NK079(dzu)003:285: 'dod pa'i yon tan rnam pa lnga ni /
NK079(dzu)003:286: mchod pa rnam pa lnga'i rang bzhin bas /
NK079(dzu)003:287: 'dod chags ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'o //
NK079(dzu)003:288: zhe sdang gtum khro thugs rje chen po'i stobs //
NK079(dzu)003:289: stong pa bdag med pa'i don dang sbyar nas /
NK079(dzu)003:290: sems can log par phyogs pa dag /h'u gis rnam par shes pa bsdus /
NK079(dzu)003:291: ho ye shes kyi rlung gis btags te /
NK079(dzu)003:292: dmigs su med pa'i don la sbyor zhing /
NK079(dzu)003:294: zhe sdang gis sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK079(dzu)003:295: gti mug gi chos thams cad mi rtog pa'i khongs su 'dus pas /
NK079(dzu)003:297: de lta bas na dug gsum ma spangs par /
NK079(dzu)003:298: sku gsum du gyur pas nye lam mo //
NK079(dzu)003:299: rnam pa gcig tu nyan thos kyi ltar byas na /
NK079(dzu)003:300: khams gsum gyi nyon mongs pa bsgom pas spang bar bya ba 'ba' zhig kyang /
NK079(dzu)003:301: brgya dgu bcu rtsa brgyad yod de de dag spangs na dgra bcom pa'i 'bras bu thob bo //
NK079(dzu)003:302: de nas sdod shes bya'i sgrib pa spong ste /
NK079(dzu)003:303: bskal ba grangs med pas chos mnyam pa nyid rtogs nas sangs rgyas so //
NK079(dzu)003:304: de ltar chos mnyam pa nyid rtogs nas /
NK079(dzu)003:305: nyan thos kyi ltar kun nas nyon mongs pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:306: rnam par byang ba'i chos so sor lta zhing /
NK079(dzu)003:308: rnam par byang ba'i chos thob bar 'dod pa lta bu ni yin gyi /
NK079(dzu)003:309: rim gyis spang du med de /
NK079(dzu)003:310: kun nas nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin med par rig nas /
NK079(dzu)003:311: rnam par byang ba yin pas /
NK079(dzu)003:313: dper na nyi ma shar nas yul khams rgyud de shar ba ni ma yin gyi /
NK079(dzu)003:314: 'dzam bu gling dus gcig du lhag gis 'char ba dang 'dra bar /
NK079(dzu)003:315: chos mnyam pa nyid du rig nas //
NK079(dzu)003:316: sgrib pa rim gyis spang du med de /
NK079(dzu)003:317: thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang dus gcig tu thob bo zhes pa'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:319: sems can drangs ba'i thabs bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig gsungs te /
NK079(dzu)003:320: de dag gi nang nas dam pa 'di yin no //
NK079(dzu)003:321: de bas na 'di las 'byung ba bzhin bsgrubs na /
NK079(dzu)003:322: tshe 'di nyid la ye shes mnyam pa nyid kyi klong chen du gyur nas /
NK079(dzu)003:323: sangs rgyas kyi sa phyi mar bsdad mi dgos te tshe 'di nyid la grub bo //
NK079(dzu)003:324: nyan thos ltar dge ba ni rung //
NK079(dzu)003:325: mi dge ba ni sgrib pa 'dod pa lta bu ni ma yin gyi /
NK079(dzu)003:326: ci ltar dpyod kyang bsod nams dang //
NK079(dzu)003:328: zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:329: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad phreng gi bden
NK079(dzu)003:330: pa gnyis bstan pa'i le'u ste dang po'o ////da ni
NK079(dzu)003:331: sgor 'jug pa 'tsham tshim bstan pa'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)003:332: sems dpa' chen po dam tshig ni //
NK079(dzu)003:333: bdag dang gzhan la phan phyir ngas bshad do //
NK079(dzu)003:335: gti mug zhe sdang nga rgyal /
NK079(dzu)003:338: bsrung du med pa'i sdom pa can //
NK079(dzu)003:339: de ni dam tshig rdo rje yin //
NK079(dzu)003:341: gti mug ni rnam par snang mdzad kyi dam tshig ste /
NK079(dzu)003:343: ma rig pa ni spang du med /
NK079(dzu)003:344: rig pa ni bsgrub tu med /
NK079(dzu)003:345: chos kyi dbyings su ro gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK079(dzu)003:346: zhe sdang ni mi 'khrung ba'i dam tshig ste /
NK079(dzu)003:347: chos kyi dbyings las kyang ma grub par thams cad du 'dus pa'i phyir ro //
NK079(dzu)003:348: nga rgyal ni rin chen 'byung ldan gyi dam tshig ste /
NK079(dzu)003:349: chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du bden par rig nas /
NK079(dzu)003:350: de la sran tshug pa'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:351: 'dod chags ni snang ba mtha' yas kyi dam tshig ste /
NK079(dzu)003:352: thams cad dbang du byed pa'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:353: phrag dog ni thams cad gdon mi za bar grub pa'i dam tshig ste /
NK079(dzu)003:354: chos mnyam par ma rtogs pas /
NK079(dzu)003:355: dge sdig yod pa'i phyir phrag dog go //
NK079(dzu)003:356: mdor na chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du chud de /
NK079(dzu)003:357: rang rig pa'i ye shes can du gyur na bsrung ba dang mi bsrung ba med de /
NK079(dzu)003:358: thams cad chos kyi klong du gyur pas /
NK079(dzu)003:359: grub pa yin pa'i phyir bsrung du med kyi /
NK079(dzu)003:360: ma grub cing sems la ye shes nyams pa med bzhin du dam tshig ma bsrungs na /
NK079(dzu)003:361: dmyal ba'i yang gting du 'gyur te //
NK079(dzu)003:362: mnyam pa'i ye shes ma rtogs pas //
NK079(dzu)003:363: mnyam la bskur ba btab pa yin no //
NK079(dzu)003:365: dag pa rnam pa gsum ste /
NK079(dzu)003:367: log par bya ba'i gnya' gnon du /
NK079(dzu)003:370: chos la dge sdig med pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:371: zas la gtsang sme med pa'i dam tshig ma nyams na /
NK079(dzu)003:373: de'i skyon gyi mi gos pa ni lus rdo rje zhes bya /
NK079(dzu)003:374: ngag gis sna tshogs smras kyang /
NK079(dzu)003:375: nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'i phyir ngag rdo rje zhes bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:376: de ltar rig pa ni sems rdo rje zhes bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:377: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng ba las /
NK079(dzu)003:378: dam tshig bstan pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o ////da ni
NK079(dzu)003:379: dkyil 'khor gsum sems dpa' chen po dbang 'di dag
NK079(dzu)003:380: ni / rang gi rig pa'i rtsal gyis thob bo //
NK079(dzu)003:382: dkyil 'khor rnam gsum gyi tshul gyis //
NK079(dzu)003:383: chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rig pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:384: dbang rang bzhin gyi thob bo /
NK079(dzu)003:386: thabs dang shes rab dbang chen te //
NK079(dzu)003:387: rdo rje dril bu rig pas 'dzin //
NK079(dzu)003:389: 'dod pa'i chos la dbang byed pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:391: de yang ci lta bu zhe na /
NK079(dzu)003:394: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin dbang byed ces gsungs te /
NK079(dzu)003:395: rigs kyi gtso bo ni thabs te /
NK079(dzu)003:397: rigs kyi gtso bo ni shes rab ste /
NK079(dzu)003:399: de dag gi byin gyis brlabs las byang chub sems bskyed pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:401: de dpyod pa 'phags pa thams cad dang /
NK079(dzu)003:402: bdag tu tha mi dad par dpyod pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:403: sku gsum thob pa'i dbang ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:404: rdo rje ni thabs kyi rtags te /
NK079(dzu)003:405: chos thams cad la dpyod pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:406: dril bu ni shes rab kyi rtags te /
NK079(dzu)003:407: chos thams cad la sgyu mar rig pa'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)003:408: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad la /
NK079(dzu)003:409: ji ltar 'dod par dbang bsgyur zhing dpyod pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:411: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gang nas kyang //
NK079(dzu)003:412: sangs rgyas rnyed par yod mi 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)003:413: rig pa'i sems nyid sangs rgyas te //
NK079(dzu)003:414: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma tshol cig /ces 'byung ba lta bu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:415: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng ba las
NK079(dzu)003:416: dbang gi le'u ste gsum pa'o ////da ni mchod pa'i
NK079(dzu)003:418: sems dpa' chen po mchod pa'i dam pa'i mchog ni 'di ltar rig par bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:419: nyan thos las khyad par cher 'phags pa'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)003:421: ci'i phyir mchod pa dang mchod ces gsungs te /
NK079(dzu)003:422: bdag mchod kun mnyes thams cad 'brangs //
NK079(dzu)003:423: kun la phan pa'i sman yin te //
NK079(dzu)003:424: rnal 'byor bdag nyid chen po yis //
NK079(dzu)003:425: thams cad brgyan cing bza' bar bya //
NK079(dzu)003:428: stong khams kyi sems can dang /
NK079(dzu)003:429: bdag tu chos kyi dbyings mnyam pa nyid kyi so
NK079(dzu)003:430: so ma yin tha mi dad par rig pa'i rnal
NK079(dzu)003:431: 'byor pas / bdag nyid zhal zas 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga rtag tu spyod de /
NK079(dzu)003:432: bdag tshim pas 'phags pa thams cad mnyes par gyur pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:433: 'di lta bu'i byin gyis brlabs kyis khams gsum gyi
NK079(dzu)003:434: sems can thams cad kyang 'drangs shing dga' bas rnal
NK079(dzu)003:435: 'byor pas ni / dus thams cad du mchod pa dang //
NK079(dzu)003:438: bdag so so ma yin pa'i ting nge 'dzin lus kyi nang du ni yi ge b+h+r+aum las /
NK079(dzu)003:439: gzhal med khang du gyur pa'i dbus na /
NK079(dzu)003:440: 'phags pa rnams bzhugs par gsal bar dmigs te /
NK079(dzu)003:442: lce ni las gang bya ba'i gtso bo dang bcas pa /
NK079(dzu)003:443: lag pa ni hom gzar du dmigs te /
NK079(dzu)003:444: de ltar phun sum tshogs pa'i don yin pas //
NK079(dzu)003:445: bdag nyid khyad par du 'phags pa'i sems dang ldan pas /
NK079(dzu)003:446: bdag ma nor ba'i dbang phyug chen po yin pa'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:447: zhal zas dang rgyan gyis brgyan par bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:448: zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:449: 'phags pa pad+mo phreng gi don las mchod pa'i le'u
NK079(dzu)003:450: ste bzhi pa'o ////da ni dkyil 'khor gsum phye ste
NK079(dzu)003:451: bshad par bya'o // kun tu 'od kyi sa las 'das //
NK079(dzu)003:452: pad+mo spyan du gyur pas ni //
NK079(dzu)003:453: rig pa'i byin rlabs chen po las //
NK079(dzu)003:456: chos kyi sku ni kun tu khyab par gnas so //
NK079(dzu)003:457: de las 'das par khyab pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:458: ma chags pa'i spyan gyis chos kyi sku la bltas na /
NK079(dzu)003:459: ji lta bu'i tshul du yang ma mthong ba //
NK079(dzu)003:461: 'bad pa med par rig pa'i byin brlabs las rang 'od kyi 'du 'phro ltar byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:462: dang po yang chos kyi sku'i byin gyis brlabs pas 'byung /
NK079(dzu)003:466: de ltar 'byung ba gang bcas na //
NK079(dzu)003:468: yi ge tshogs chen 'khor lo ste //
NK079(dzu)003:469: mtshan dang dpe byad kun las 'phro //
NK079(dzu)003:470: rang bzhin 'dum pa'i gzugs can dang //
NK079(dzu)003:471: mgyogs pa mgyogs ma'i pho nyar ldan zhes gsungs te /
NK079(dzu)003:472: yi ge 'bru lnga pos mtshan pa las /
NK079(dzu)003:473: ye shes lnga las gtso bo rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK079(dzu)003:477: gdon mi za bar grub pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:478: ye shes lnga'i yul lnga nas /
NK079(dzu)003:479: gtso bo kun tu bzang po dang /
NK079(dzu)003:484: de'i byin gyis brlabs pa las /
NK079(dzu)003:485: byung ba ni rtsa gnyis dang sbyar //
NK079(dzu)003:488: bcu drug gnyis ni sum cu rtsa gnyis te /
NK079(dzu)003:489: mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang sbyar /
NK079(dzu)003:491: dbu rgyan lta bu'i rigs lnga lnga zhig 'byung ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:492: spyir brgyad cu ste dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang sbyar ro //
NK079(dzu)003:493: sems ma la dbu rgyan yod kyi /
NK079(dzu)003:494: gnyis kyi byin gyis brlabs las 'byung bas /
NK079(dzu)003:495: dpe byad kyi skabs su bshad /
NK079(dzu)003:496: rtsis las 'das pa'i nang du rtogs so //
NK079(dzu)003:497: rig pa'i byin rlabs las byung ba'i sems dang /
NK079(dzu)003:498: sems las ma gtogs pa'i mtshan dang dpe byad ni /
NK079(dzu)003:499: 'khor lo bskor ba'i rgyal po yang yod de /
NK079(dzu)003:500: de ni sangs rgyas ma yin no //
NK079(dzu)003:501: khro bo dang khro mo rnams ni //
NK079(dzu)003:503: khro zhing gtum pa de rtag chad kyi mtha' la khro gtum zhes bya ba'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:504: pho nya ni 'gro ba med pa kun tu phyin pa ste /
NK079(dzu)003:505: chos kyi dbyings dang tha mi dad pa'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:506: 'di dag 'bad rtsol med pa rang 'byung bas /
NK079(dzu)003:507: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:508: de la 'di ni thig le rdo rje yin //
NK079(dzu)003:509: 'di nas gang zag bdag med pa //
NK079(dzu)003:510: rtogs par bya phyir ngas bshad de //
NK079(dzu)003:511: mkhas pas de la sbyor bar gyis //
NK079(dzu)003:513: de la thig le ni chos kyi dbyings so //
NK079(dzu)003:514: rdo rje ni lha dang lha mo'i tshul du yod pa la bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:515: don tu na rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:516: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor 'di bshad pas /
NK079(dzu)003:517: gang zag la bdag med par rtogs pa'i phyir bshad do //
NK079(dzu)003:520: lha dang lha mo'i tshul du ji ltar 'byung bar rtogs pa 'am /
NK079(dzu)003:521: 'byor par gyis shig pa'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:522: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng ba las /
NK079(dzu)003:523: ting 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi le'u ste lnga pa'o
NK079(dzu)003:524: ////da ni gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir
NK079(dzu)003:525: / sems dpa' spyod yul thams cad ni /
NK079(dzu)003:528: chen po lnga la de bzhin gshegs pa gcig la lnga lngar rig par gyis /
NK079(dzu)003:529: khams gsum bdag nyid yin pa ste //
NK079(dzu)003:530: sku gsum zhes kyang de la bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:531: nam mkha' rnam par snang mdzad /
NK079(dzu)003:535: rlung gdon mi za bar grub pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:536: sa gcig pu la yang sra ba dang /
NK079(dzu)003:540: nam mkha' bag ma zhi bas lnga lnga yod de /
NK079(dzu)003:541: de bzhiin du lhag ma rnams la de bzhin du rig par bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:542: de ni sems dpa' dang sems ma'i mtshan nyid do //
NK079(dzu)003:545: yid ni gzugs med pa'i khams /
NK079(dzu)003:546: lus ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yin /
NK079(dzu)003:547: sems ni chos kyi sku yin /
NK079(dzu)003:550: ye shes dang ni 'gro ba lnga //
NK079(dzu)003:551: mnyam pas so so dbyer med de //
NK079(dzu)003:552: sngags dang phyag rgyas dbang bskur bas //
NK079(dzu)003:553: spyod lam kun du ma 'da' la zhes gsungs te /
NK079(dzu)003:554: de ltar mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:556: bdag so so ma yin par rigs pas sangs rgyas gud na dpyod mi dgos /
NK079(dzu)003:557: ngag smras so cog sngags yin pas //
NK079(dzu)003:558: snying po lhag par brjod du med //
NK079(dzu)003:559: lus bskyod do cog phyag rgya yin pas /
NK079(dzu)003:560: phyag rgyas bsrung mi dgos te /
NK079(dzu)003:562: bdag nyid chen po'i rig pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal chen po /
NK079(dzu)003:564: dper na dbang po lnga ni yab lnga /
NK079(dzu)003:565: yul lnga ni yum lnga ste /
NK079(dzu)003:566: lus ni be ro tsa na /
NK079(dzu)003:568: rna ba ni a mi de ba /
NK079(dzu)003:569: sna ni rad na sam b+ha ba /
NK079(dzu)003:570: lce ni e mo ka si ti /
NK079(dzu)003:571: gzugs thams cad ni rdo rje sge mo /
NK079(dzu)003:572: sgra thams cad ni rdo rje dbyangs /
NK079(dzu)003:573: dri thams cad ni rdo rje phreng ba /
NK079(dzu)003:574: ro thams cad ni rdo rje gar ro //
NK079(dzu)003:575: reg thams cad ni kun tu bzang mo //
NK079(dzu)003:577: bdag gi byin brlabs thams cad 'dus shing /
NK079(dzu)003:578: tshogs pa'i phyir tshogs zhes bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:579: dkyil ces bya ba gang zhe na /
NK079(dzu)003:580: thams cad bdag gi sems las sprul pa'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)003:581: ye shes thams cad chos nyid dag pa las sprul pas /
NK079(dzu)003:582: chos dang sems dang rig pas mnyam par gyur pa las /
NK079(dzu)003:585: thams cad dbus mtha' med par ye shes kyis khyab cing rdzogs par spyod pa ni 'khor zhes bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:586: de lta bu ni tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:588: sgo lnga'i rnam par shes pa rang 'thad du ma 'phros te /
NK079(dzu)003:591: rnam par shes pa zhes bya ste //
NK079(dzu)003:593: dkyil 'khor thams cad 'byung ba'i rgyu yin no //
NK079(dzu)003:594: de la sems kyi rang bzhin kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa la /
NK079(dzu)003:595: bag chags sna tshogs pa bsags pas gnas gyur te /
NK079(dzu)003:596: bsod nams kyi zhing dag pa ni //
NK079(dzu)003:597: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'i ye shes te /
NK079(dzu)003:598: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs so //
NK079(dzu)003:599: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa phyi nang gi 'jig rten la /
NK079(dzu)003:600: rgyun mi chad par rtogs shing sna tshogs kyi rang bzhin du 'jug pa nyid /
NK079(dzu)003:602: ye shes su 'phros pas rnam par dag pa'i thabs su rig cing /
NK079(dzu)003:603: gnas su gyur pa ni me long lta bu'i ye shes rdo rje'i rigs so //
NK079(dzu)003:604: nyon mongs pa'i yid bdag tu lta ba gnas su
NK079(dzu)003:605: gyur pa ni mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes te
NK079(dzu)003:607: sgo lnga'i rnam par shes pa rang thad du ma 'phros te /
NK079(dzu)003:608: ye shes su blta bas su rnam par dag pa'i thabs su rig cing gnas gyur pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:609: bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes te las kyi rigs so //
NK079(dzu)003:610: yid kyi rnam par shes pa gzung 'dzin ngang du rtog pa can /
NK079(dzu)003:611: yul la rang thad du ma 'phros pas /
NK079(dzu)003:612: rnam par dag pa'i thabs su rig cing gnas gyur pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:613: pad+ma ltar thabs kyis sgo sna tshogs kyis /
NK079(dzu)003:614: so sor kun tu rtogs pa'i ye shes te pad+ma'i rigs so //
NK079(dzu)003:615: ye shes su bltas pas ni /
NK079(dzu)003:616: rnam par dag pa'i thabs su rig pas /
NK079(dzu)003:617: kun tu lta ba'i bsnol te khang ni rab sbyar nas //
NK079(dzu)003:618: ldan pa g.yas su byo ba las /
NK079(dzu)003:619: chags pa'i tshul gyis blta ba las //
NK079(dzu)003:620: rdo rje 'bebs pa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK079(dzu)003:621: lag gnyis thal mo mnyam sbyar nas //
NK079(dzu)003:622: sor mo brgyab tu bsnol nas su //
NK079(dzu)003:623: gung mo gnyis bshibs bsgreng ba ni //
NK079(dzu)003:624: rdo rje sems dpa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK079(dzu)003:625: lag gnyis sor mo bsnol nas su //
NK079(dzu)003:626: gung mo gnyis kyi rtse mo rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:627: myu gu'i tshul du bkug pa ni //
NK079(dzu)003:628: rdo rje rin chen mo'i rgya //
NK079(dzu)003:629: lag gnyis sor mo rnams bsnol te //
NK079(dzu)003:630: phan tshun gsum po bsdom pa las //
NK079(dzu)003:631: gung mo bar du bkug bsnol nas //
NK079(dzu)003:632: rdo rje las ma'i phyag rgya yin //
NK079(dzu)003:633: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng ba las /
NK079(dzu)003:634: phyag rgya'i le'u ste bcu pa'o ////da ni rigs sngags gcod pa'i le'u bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:635: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang /
NK079(dzu)003:636: lha mo rnams la phyag na rdo rje la sogs pa byang chub sems dpa' brgyad dang /
NK079(dzu)003:637: 'khor phal po che dbyangs dang mthun par bstod nas /
NK079(dzu)003:639: rgyal ba gang bzhugs 'khor dang bcas //
NK079(dzu)003:640: bla med lha lnga lha mo yi //
NK079(dzu)003:641: grub pa'i byin rlabs bsam mi khyab //
NK079(dzu)003:642: sems dpa' bcu drug rigs kyi gtso //
NK079(dzu)003:643: sems ma bcu drug rigs kyi yum //
NK079(dzu)003:644: mthu chen khro bo khro mo dang //
NK079(dzu)003:645: pho nya 'jig rten skyong dang ldan //
NK079(dzu)003:646: sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni //
NK079(dzu)003:647: 'jig rten ma lus thams cad kun //
NK079(dzu)003:648: rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyor bas na //
NK079(dzu)003:649: phyag rgya chen po bdag sbyor cig /
NK079(dzu)003:650: dpa' bo chen po mthur ldan rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:651: thugs rje chen po'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK079(dzu)003:652: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:653: 'grub par byin gyis brlabs tu gsol //
NK079(dzu)003:654: khams gsum zhing du sbyor la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:655: dmigs med chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:656: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:657: cir yang sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:658: zhes bstod nas nyid kyi thugs kar zhugs te /
NK079(dzu)003:659: rol pa khro bo zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas /
NK079(dzu)003:660: khro bo'i rtog pa bshad do //
NK079(dzu)003:661: de nas bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' la /
NK079(dzu)003:662: lag na rdo rjes 'di skad ces gsol to //
NK079(dzu)003:664: ma 'ongs ba'i dus na gcer bu pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:665: kun tu rgyu la sogs pas /
NK079(dzu)003:666: so so'i rigs sngags kyi las kyis /
NK079(dzu)003:667: lha ma h+aa de ba la sogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:669: gnod sbyin mthu bo che dang /
NK079(dzu)003:671: sems can la srog gi bar chad bgyid 'tshe bar bgyid /
NK079(dzu)003:672: shin tu sdug bsngal bar bgyid na /
NK079(dzu)003:673: de thabs gang gis bzlog par bgyid //
NK079(dzu)003:676: lag na rdo rje nyon cig /
NK079(dzu)003:677: 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku dang gsung dang /
NK079(dzu)003:678: thugs rdo rje'i bdag pos sngon yang bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:679: lag na rdo rje khyod kyis byas pa'i gsang sngags dang /
NK079(dzu)003:680: srid pa zad par bya ba'i gsang sngags thams cad kyang bzlog par byed /
NK079(dzu)003:682: kun tu rgyu la sogs pa gzhan lta ci smos /
NK079(dzu)003:683: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis rdo rje mtshon cha'i /
NK079(dzu)003:684: ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas /
NK079(dzu)003:685: sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las /
NK079(dzu)003:686: gsang sngags bzlos shing gnon pa dang //
NK079(dzu)003:687: sbyor ba gcod pa zhes bya ba 'di gsungs so //
NK079(dzu)003:692: h'u bru tru bru tra bru a bru /
NK079(dzu)003:694: phyogs bcu nas mtshon cha'i char chen po bab pas /
NK079(dzu)003:695: lag na rdo rje nyid kha sbub tu 'gyel nas /
NK079(dzu)003:696: khrag tu skyugs par gyur to //
NK079(dzu)003:697: lha dang gnod sbyin thams cad brgyal te /
NK079(dzu)003:698: lus dum bur chad par gyur to //
NK079(dzu)003:700: de dag gi sbyor ba chad par rig nas /
NK079(dzu)003:702: badz+ra swa da t+wa ra dza dz+ha /
NK079(dzu)003:704: lag na rdo rje la bka' stsal pa /
NK079(dzu)003:705: lag na rdo rje khyod nyid kyang /
NK079(dzu)003:706: 'di las 'da' bar ma byed cig /khyod kyis 'khor thams cad kyang 'di las 'da' bar na /
NK079(dzu)003:708: de bzhin du lag na rdo rje khyod kyis /
NK079(dzu)003:709: lha dang gnod sbyin thams cad la yang bsgo zhig /de nas lag na rdo rjes gsol ba /
NK079(dzu)003:710: bcom ldan 'das 'di na srid gsum 'du bar bgyid pa /
NK079(dzu)003:711: mthu bo che thams cad kyi nga rgyal gcod pa dag lags te /
NK079(dzu)003:712: ci ltar bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pas /
NK079(dzu)003:713: mthu stobs dang ldan pa'i slad du /
NK079(dzu)003:714: bdag gi ming lag na rdo rje zhes btags nas /
NK079(dzu)003:715: 'dir rdo rje sems dpas bcom ldan 'das kyis byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK079(dzu)003:717: bdag kyang khrag tu skyugs cing 'gyel bar gyur na /
NK079(dzu)003:720: gnod sbyin rnams la yang sgo'o //
NK079(dzu)003:721: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis ma 'ongs pa'i dus na /
NK079(dzu)003:722: gsang sngags 'di grub pa'i cho ga bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:723: la las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor du dpal chen khrag 'thung spyan drang pa /
NK079(dzu)003:724: sku ni dud ka chen mo la //
NK079(dzu)003:725: dbu skra khams nag ral pa can //
NK079(dzu)003:726: dbu gsum po la phyag drug ste //
NK079(dzu)003:727: dmar dang dud ka gnag pa'i yin //
NK079(dzu)003:728: g.yas kyi gsum na thogs pa ni //
NK079(dzu)003:729: sti ra'i dbyug pa chen po dang //
NK079(dzu)003:730: dung chen dmar gyis bskang ba la //
NK079(dzu)003:731: rdo rjes dkrug cing 'thung bar brtag /g.yon gyi gsum na thogs pa ni //
NK079(dzu)003:732: sti ra'i rgyu ma thogs pa dang //
NK079(dzu)003:733: khyung gi khra chen thogs pa dang //
NK079(dzu)003:734: sti ra khra mo'i gsum pa nas //
NK079(dzu)003:735: glo snying nang khrol 'dren cing za //
NK079(dzu)003:736: gtsug tu rnam par snang mdzad //
NK079(dzu)003:737: phrag pa g.yas pa a k+sho b+h+ye h'u /
NK079(dzu)003:738: g.yon na rat+na sam b+ham ba tram /
NK079(dzu)003:739: rkang pa g.yas na a mo si ti a //
NK079(dzu)003:740: g.yon na a mi de ba h+r+ai /
NK079(dzu)003:741: brum las rdo rje 'khor lo dang //
NK079(dzu)003:742: rdo rje rnams ni rigs sngags brtag /kee ri dang ni tsi'u ri dang //
NK079(dzu)003:743: bra mo ha dang pe ta li //
NK079(dzu)003:744: gzhan yang bya tri mu ka dang //
NK079(dzu)003:746: sri la mu ka la sogs mgyogs ma rnams /
NK079(dzu)003:747: sti ra la ni 'bru tshugs su //
NK079(dzu)003:748: lta zhing rtod pa'i tshul las ni //
NK079(dzu)003:749: ta ha de nas skad cig yud tsam la //
NK079(dzu)003:750: sngags nyid dang spong gtong bcas te //
NK079(dzu)003:751: 'gugs pa'i pho nyar brtag par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:752: ras sam gro ba 'am r+ts+wa rnams la //
NK079(dzu)003:753: khro ba'i gzugs su bris pa'am //
NK079(dzu)003:754: yang na rkud pa nag pos bcing //
NK079(dzu)003:755: ha ha'i gad mo chen po dang //
NK079(dzu)003:756: rdo rje bskul ba'i glu blangs te //
NK079(dzu)003:757: pho nya rnams kyang mngag par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:758: de na rigs sngags bzung nas kyang //
NK079(dzu)003:759: rtsa'i gzugs la gnas pa dang //
NK079(dzu)003:760: 'khor lo la sogs mtshon cha yis //
NK079(dzu)003:761: de dag phye mar brlag pa ra bya //
NK079(dzu)003:763: phye ma de dag gtubs nas kyang //
NK079(dzu)003:764: thod pa gzhu dang bcas pa yis //
NK079(dzu)003:765: hmo khung gru gsum sgo can du //
NK079(dzu)003:766: ram zhes bya ba'i me sbar nas //
NK079(dzu)003:767: drang srong 'khor rnams g.yab mos bod //
NK079(dzu)003:768: de nas rigs sngags sreg par byed //
NK079(dzu)003:769: de dag dang bdag sbyang nas /
NK079(dzu)003:770: rnam lnga'i chas dang ldan par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:771: ma mo chen mo sha la spyon //
NK079(dzu)003:772: 'byung po sha ni zan bas zhim //
NK079(dzu)003:773: 'byung po'i khrag ni chang bas zhim //
NK079(dzu)003:774: ma mo chen mo khrag la spyon //
NK079(dzu)003:775: ma mo chen mo rkang la spyon //
NK079(dzu)003:776: 'byung po'i rkang ni mar bas zhim //
NK079(dzu)003:777: 'byung po'i rus pa zhim ba ste //
NK079(dzu)003:778: 'di dag gsol te mnyes par mdzod //
NK079(dzu)003:779: glu dang gar dang gad rgyang gyis //
NK079(dzu)003:780: so sor mchod de bsgrub par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:781: zin pa'i sems can gang yang rung //
NK079(dzu)003:782: de dag rkud pa nag pos bcang //
NK079(dzu)003:783: de yang dum bu gcad par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:784: de nas mi de snga ma bzhin //
NK079(dzu)003:785: tshe gnas bya phyir 'bru lnga yi //
NK079(dzu)003:786: gnas lnga dag tu rnam bkod de //
NK079(dzu)003:787: zin pa'i sems can bsrung bar bya //
NK079(dzu)003:788: tsha zhing rtsub bo'i shing dang ni //
NK079(dzu)003:789: sha dang chang dang yo byad rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:790: gnag cing tsha ba rnams sbyar te //
NK079(dzu)003:791: lha chen rnams la mchod pa bya //
NK079(dzu)003:792: de nas las rnams grub pa dang //
NK079(dzu)003:793: ha ha la sogs gad mo dang //
NK079(dzu)003:794: glu dang rdo rje dbyug pa yis //
NK079(dzu)003:795: lha rnams dag la thim par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:796: 'di ni bdag nyid bsrung ba dang //
NK079(dzu)003:797: las rnams thams cad grub par byed //
NK079(dzu)003:798: shar phyogs na phra man ma ke'u ri ma /
NK079(dzu)003:799: kha dog sngon mo phyag gnyis te //
NK079(dzu)003:800: phyag g.yas pa na ban d+ha tsan dan dmar pos bskang ba thogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:801: g.yon zhing chung gi dbyug pa thogs pa ste /
NK079(dzu)003:802: badz+ra kam ri dza dza h'u /
NK079(dzu)003:803: zhes stong rtsa brgyad bzlas te bcol nas /
NK079(dzu)003:806: che ge mo zhig khug cig ces bcol lo //
NK079(dzu)003:807: gtor ma tsan dan dmar chen gyis arga la /
NK079(dzu)003:808: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo /
NK079(dzu)003:809: zhes brjod cing arga lan gsum sbreng ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:810: lho phyogs na tso ri kha dog ser mo /
NK079(dzu)003:812: badz+ra tso ri ha dza dza /
NK079(dzu)003:813: zhes stong rtsa brgyad bzlas te bcol na /
NK079(dzu)003:814: phyag na rdo rje'i mthu yang 'phrog nus na /
NK079(dzu)003:815: gzhan lta smos kyang ci dgos /
NK079(dzu)003:816: nub phyogs na phra mo ha /
NK079(dzu)003:818: phyag na chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan thogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:819: badz+ra pra mo ha dza dza /
NK079(dzu)003:820: zhes brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas te bcol na /
NK079(dzu)003:821: phyag na rdo rje yang rang bzhin gyi mthu gzhan nas dbang du 'ong nas /
NK079(dzu)003:822: gzhan lta smos kyang ci dgos /
NK079(dzu)003:823: byang phyogs na pe ta li /
NK079(dzu)003:825: phyag g.yon zhing chung 'dzin cing za ba /
NK079(dzu)003:826: phyag g.yas na rdo rje 'phyar ba /
NK079(dzu)003:827: badz+ra pe ta li h'u dza dza /
NK079(dzu)003:828: zhes rtsa brgyad bzlas te bcol na /
NK079(dzu)003:829: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dngos grub thams cad kyang 'grub na /
NK079(dzu)003:830: 'jig rten gyi bsgrub pa phran tshegs lta ci smos /
NK079(dzu)003:831: shar lho mtshams nas bu ka si kha dog dmar ser /
NK079(dzu)003:832: phyag gnyis zhing chung gi ba su ta 'dren cing za ba /
NK079(dzu)003:833: badz+ra pu ka si h'u dza dza /
NK079(dzu)003:834: zhes bzlas te bcol na phyag na rdo rje yang 'chi zhing 'dren par nus na /
NK079(dzu)003:839: phyag g.yon ban d+ha tsan dan dmar pos bkang ste /
NK079(dzu)003:841: badz+ra kas ma ri h'u dza dza /
NK079(dzu)003:842: zhes stong rtsa brgyad bzlas te bcol na /
NK079(dzu)003:843: phyag na rdo rje yang myos par 'gyur na /
NK079(dzu)003:844: gzhan lta smos kyang ci dgos /
NK079(dzu)003:846: badz+ra sma sha ni kha dog ljang gu /
NK079(dzu)003:847: zhing chung lag pa gnyis kyis bzung ste /
NK079(dzu)003:849: badz+ra sma sha ni h'u dza dza /
NK079(dzu)003:852: za ma dang ma ning yang rgyud 'phel bar 'gyur na /
NK079(dzu)003:853: dbang po tshang zhing nyams pa med pa lta ci smos /
NK079(dzu)003:854: tshe dang dbang thang 'phel bar bya ba lta ci smos /
NK079(dzu)003:855: 'phra men ma 'di rnams 'phrin las mdzad par bskul ba'i tshe /
NK079(dzu)003:856: arga dang gtor ma dbul ba ni gong du smos pa bzhin du tshul bzhin du bgyi /
NK079(dzu)003:857: khros nas thams cad kyi phyag cha tri shul 'bar ba /
NK079(dzu)003:859: gdan me smug nag gi steng na bzhugs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:860: sku'i kha dog nag po la /
NK079(dzu)003:861: khrag dang zhag dang thal ba'i thig les tshom bur byas shing /
NK079(dzu)003:862: ba su tas rked pa bcings pa /
NK079(dzu)003:863: gser gyi pags pa gos su gyon pa /
NK079(dzu)003:864: sro ta a 'dzas lus brgyan te /
NK079(dzu)003:865: gcer bu'i tshogs smug nag 'bar ba /
NK079(dzu)003:867: gdan me smug nag 'jig rten gyi khams zad cing bsreg par byas nas /
NK079(dzu)003:868: slar dpal chen po'i skur thim par byas so //
NK079(dzu)003:869: de'i phyir rim par bshad par byas te /
NK079(dzu)003:870: shar phyogs nas seng ha mu ka /kha dog ser mo zhi kha na thogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:871: lag pa g.yas g.yon bsnol ba /
NK079(dzu)003:873: lho phyogs na be kri mu ka /kha dog dmar po /
NK079(dzu)003:875: mdun na zhing gnas pa la blta ba stag gi mgo can /
NK079(dzu)003:876: nub phyogs na sri la mu ka kha dog nag po /
NK079(dzu)003:877: lag pa gnyis na zhing chung 'dzin lces ldag pa /
NK079(dzu)003:879: byang phyogs na shwa na mu ka /kha dog mthing nag /zhing lag pa gnyis kyis khong bral te /
NK079(dzu)003:882: kri ta mu ka /kha dog dmar nag /zhing chung ngu'i ba su ta kha na thogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:883: lag pa g.yas na ban d+ha /
NK079(dzu)003:886: lho nub mtshams na kang ka mu ga /kha dog
NK079(dzu)003:887: dmar ba lag pa g.yas pa la zhing 'gel zhing
NK079(dzu)003:890: bya rkang ka'i mgo can mchu ring ba /
NK079(dzu)003:891: thor to bkug pa ze ba dmar ba /
NK079(dzu)003:893: kha kha mu ka kha dog nag mo /
NK079(dzu)003:895: lag pa g.yas pa pad+ma b+han d+ha 'dzin pa /
NK079(dzu)003:896: byang shar gyi mtshams su hu lu mu ka /kha dog sna tshogs /
NK079(dzu)003:897: lag pa g.yas pa dung chen khrag gis bkang ba 'thung ba /
NK079(dzu)003:898: g.yon pa rdo rje lcags kyu 'dzin pa 'ug pa'i mgo can /
NK079(dzu)003:899: nang rim 'ug pa'i 'khor gyis bskor ba /
NK079(dzu)003:900: de'i phyi rim bya rog gi 'khor gyi bskor ba
NK079(dzu)003:901: de'i phyi rim bya rkang ka'i 'khor gyis bskor ba
NK079(dzu)003:902: / de'i phyi rim bya rgod kyi 'khor gyis bskor ba /
NK079(dzu)003:903: de dag thams cad kyang zhing mang po gsar rnying spungs pa'i steng na /
NK079(dzu)003:905: 'thab pa'i tshul ston pa sha dag go //
NK079(dzu)003:906: de dag gi snying po ni 'di rnams so //
NK079(dzu)003:908: 'di kun 'bru re re la yang lan bzhi bzhi brjod do //
NK079(dzu)003:910: has nang gi lha mo bskyed /
NK079(dzu)003:911: hes phyi'i lha mo brgyad bskyed /
NK079(dzu)003:912: phata kyis thams cad khro bor bskul /
NK079(dzu)003:913: h'u gis thams cad 'od zer 'bar bas /
NK079(dzu)003:915: lha mo 'od ldan tshogs kyi bdag /he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:916: slob dpon lha ni brnyas byed dang /
NK079(dzu)003:917: rnal 'byor bar du gcod pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:918: dam tshig gnyan po 'dral ba dang /
NK079(dzu)003:919: rdo rje spun la 'khu ba rnams /
NK079(dzu)003:920: khyod kyis rdul du brlag nas ni //
NK079(dzu)003:921: gnod sems ma lus gtan nas phyung /
NK079(dzu)003:922: dpal chen ta na 'ga' na'i tshogs chen po la gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK079(dzu)003:923: sku gsung thugs kyi khro bo gzi brjid kyis /
NK079(dzu)003:924: gdug pa thams cad gtan nas 'byin cing /
NK079(dzu)003:925: longs spyod chen po'i tshogs chen po la /
NK079(dzu)003:927: thams cad dgyes par mdzad pa yi //
NK079(dzu)003:929: rdo rje pad+ma'i phyag rgya dpal 'bar bcing nas phyar te mchod cing /
NK079(dzu)003:930: 'khor thams cad gcer bur phyung nas /
NK079(dzu)003:931: skra bshig cing rgyug ste sngags 'di gsung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:932: e a ra li ho hrim hrim hrim /
NK079(dzu)003:933: de nas tshogs su gshegs nas /
NK079(dzu)003:934: 'khor thams cad la spyan bsgrad nas //
NK079(dzu)003:935: gzigs shing 'dzum pa'i brdas ha ha sang sang sgra phyung ste /
NK079(dzu)003:937: mgrin cig tu dbyangs 'di gtso bo la bstod do //
NK079(dzu)003:941: chos don dag pa bdag med pa //
NK079(dzu)003:942: nam mkha' dang ni mnyam pa'i gnas //
NK079(dzu)003:943: rdo rje rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:944: zhes brjod pas gtso bo mnyes nas /
NK079(dzu)003:946: dam gsal ba'i dbyangs 'di gsungs so //
NK079(dzu)003:948: sha ta ba ka /a la la ho //
NK079(dzu)003:949: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK079(dzu)003:955: lha mo rnams rnga brdung zhing dbyangs len /
NK079(dzu)003:956: rgyud gsum gyi glu tshig /ta ke ma ta ke ma ta ke ma /
NK079(dzu)003:957: ge te ma ge te ma /
NK079(dzu)003:958: ta ke ma ta ke ma /
NK079(dzu)003:959: k+she ma k+she ma k+she ma /
NK079(dzu)003:960: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo'i phreng ba las /
NK079(dzu)003:961: rigs sngags gcod pa'i le'u sta bcu gcig pa'o ////da
NK079(dzu)003:962: ni rdo rje srin po rnams kyi dkyil 'khor bshad
NK079(dzu)003:963: do // sems dpa' chen po nyon cig ces gsungs pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:964: rdo rje srin pa'i dkyil 'khor bshad pa'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:965: rdo rje sems dpa' la bos so //
NK079(dzu)003:966: h'u bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba yi /
NK079(dzu)003:968: khro bo chen po rnams bzhugs pa //
NK079(dzu)003:969: brkyang bskum tshul du gnas pa ste //
NK079(dzu)003:971: bdud dang bgegs la stsogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:972: spa skong zhing brlagsa par 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:973: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad me dpung cher po 'bar zhing /
NK079(dzu)003:974: tug tsom gyi sgra nang du /
NK079(dzu)003:975: 'od zer sna tshogs 'phro zhing 'khyil ba'i dbus na /
NK079(dzu)003:977: zhabs brkyang bskum gyi tshul du khro gnyer sdang mig tu gzigs shing bzhugs pa'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:978: gzhan du na rtag chad kyi mtha' dang /
NK079(dzu)003:980: lta ba'i gnas drug cu rtsa gnyis ni /
NK079(dzu)003:981: yang dag pa'i dbyings nyid la 'jug pa'i bar du gcod pas /
NK079(dzu)003:983: sbyor mi rtogs par gyur pas bdud de dag 'joms shing /
NK079(dzu)003:984: skrag pa'i shes rab kyi me la bya /
NK079(dzu)003:985: ye shes lnga'i 'od zer sna lnga las /
NK079(dzu)003:986: thogs pa med par 'jug pa dang //
NK079(dzu)003:988: gnyis su med pa'i ting nge 'dzin du thims nas /
NK079(dzu)003:989: mtha' las 'das te sku mi dmigs pa dkyil lo //
NK079(dzu)003:990: don gong ma ltar go ba ni sgra te /
NK079(dzu)003:991: kun tu khyab pa'i phyir sgra chen po zhes bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:992: ye shes lnga tha dad par rig cing go ba
NK079(dzu)003:993: ni sgra sna tshogs pa yin ces gcig la spros
NK079(dzu)003:995: brkyang pa ni shes rab te /
NK079(dzu)003:996: dbyings la dmigs pa'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:998: dbyings nyid la mi dmigs par chud pa'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:999: dbus kyi khrag 'thung chen po ni //
NK079(dzu)003:1000: dbu dgu phyag rgya bco brgyad de //
NK079(dzu)003:1001: gshog pa rdo rje gtams pas gdengs //
NK079(dzu)003:1002: zhabs kyang brgyad du rnam par bstan //
NK079(dzu)003:1004: khro bo'i 'og nas 'byung ba'i dbus na he ru ka gtso bor bzhugs te /
NK079(dzu)003:1012: g.yas dmar smug /g.yon ljang nag go //
NK079(dzu)003:1013: dbu skra ral pa khams nag gyen du 'khyil ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1014: thod pa skam po'i phreng bas brgyan pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1015: sku mdog nag po zhes kyang 'byung ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1016: sku yang ni mdog dang sku cir yang 'gyur ces 'chad pa mang ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1017: thod pa rlon pa'i phreng ba se ral khar thogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1019: g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1020: rdo rje dang dung chen khrag gis bkang ba dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1022: sti ra zhing chen rlon pa'i glo snying 'byin cing gsol ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1024: sti ra chen po'i nang zhags ldogs te /
NK079(dzu)003:1025: lam rgyud lnga'i sems can thams cad la 'debs te /
NK079(dzu)003:1026: dbyings la sbyor zhing lta na byed //
NK079(dzu)003:1028: steng chung du chang par bcangs te //
NK079(dzu)003:1031: nyi ma zla ba thugs kar 'dzin //
NK079(dzu)003:1032: de'i 'og ma gnyis na cir yang 'gyur ba'i mtshon cha /
NK079(dzu)003:1034: 'phra men mgyogs ma zhes bya ba dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1035: gsod ma zhes bya ba khyung dang 'ug pa lta bur sprul pa'i khra thogs nas /
NK079(dzu)003:1036: dam las 'gal ba gtong zhes pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1038: rlung dang me'i dkyil 'khor thogs pa ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1039: 'jig rten thams cad mthong zhes bsreg go //
NK079(dzu)003:1041: chu'i dkyil 'khor dang ri thogs te /
NK079(dzu)003:1042: 'jig rten gyi khams gnod cing g.yeng bar mdzad do //
NK079(dzu)003:1045: yid bzhin gyi za ma tog te //
NK079(dzu)003:1046: rnal 'byor pa rnams la cis kyang mi tshugs pa'i go cha la sogs pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1047: dngos grub rnam gsum thob par mdzad do //
NK079(dzu)003:1048: gzhan du na ma thar gyis gnas pa'i snyoms par 'jug pa dgu /
NK079(dzu)003:1049: chos nyid dang tha mi dad la //
NK079(dzu)003:1051: stong pa bco brgyad du rig pa de nyid //
NK079(dzu)003:1052: ye shes brgyad kyi phyi nang gi dngos po 'jig pa'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:1053: phyag bco brgyad dang sbyar te /
NK079(dzu)003:1055: spyan dgu ni chos nyid las gzhan du mi gzigs so //
NK079(dzu)003:1057: stong pa bco brgyad la dmigs pas shes rab bo //
NK079(dzu)003:1058: de ltar thabs dang shes rab 'brel pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1063: sku gsung thugs kyang stong pa bco brgyad du gzigs pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1065: khro bo brgya rtsa brgyad do //
NK079(dzu)003:1066: khro bos gzigs pa'i yul gzugs dang //
NK079(dzu)003:1071: stong pa bco brgyad phrag drug ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1072: de ni dmigs pa'i yul yin pas khro bo brgya rtsa brgyad do //
NK079(dzu)003:1073: de lta bu sha stag ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1074: chos thams cad khro bo dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1075: khro mo yin par mkhas pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1077: zhes gcig las spros pa'i tan+t+ra las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1078: mkha' lding gi rgyal po'i tshul du rdo rje gshog pas gdengs pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1079: phyag mang po gdengs pa la yang zhes kyang bshad /
NK079(dzu)003:1080: gshog pa ni rdo rje stams pa ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1081: 'jig rten gdengs pa tsam du gdengs pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1082: gzhan du chos kyi dbyings las /
NK079(dzu)003:1083: ye shes 'phro ba dang thams cad du khyab pas phyin pa'i don te /
NK079(dzu)003:1084: zhabs brgyad kyi g.yas g.yon gnyis ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1085: ma h+aa ka la pho mo gnyis bardzisa pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1087: tshogs kyi bdag po pho mo gnyis bardzisa pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1089: byi na ya ga pho mo gnyis bardzisa pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1090: gzhan du rnam par thar pa brgyad la zhen pa'i tha tshig ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1092: snyoms par 'jug pa bzhi sgom zhing chos nyid ma rtogs pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1094: chos nyid rtogs pas rnam par thar pa brgyad du gyur te /
NK079(dzu)003:1095: de'i phyir 'jig rten kyi lha brgyad zhabs kyis bardzisa
NK079(dzu)003:1096: pa ni 'jig rten gyi lha'i bsam gtan chos nyid
NK079(dzu)003:1097: du mkhyen te / chos rtags pas rnam par thar pa brgyad la zhon zhes bya ba'i don te /
NK079(dzu)003:1099: dbu gsum phyag drug gshog pa can //
NK079(dzu)003:1100: zhabs drug rdo rje brag steng na //
NK079(dzu)003:1103: sh+ri he ru ka'i 'khor gyi khro bo re re la yang yan lag nyi shu rtsa bdun /
NK079(dzu)003:1104: phyag rgya lnga bcu rtsa bzhi dang ldan par bstan no //
NK079(dzu)003:1105: shar phyogs su khro bo rnam par rgyal sku mdog dkar ba dbu dbus dkar ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1107: phyag g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis ni //
NK079(dzu)003:1108: rdo rje dang dung chen dmar gyis bkang ba dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1112: sti ra'i dbyug pa dang pha bang bsnams pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1113: gshog pa ni gong du bshad pa dang mthun no //
NK079(dzu)003:1114: rdo rje brag gtams pa la brten te /
NK079(dzu)003:1115: 'jig rten skyong ba brgya byin zhabs kyis bardzisa te bzhugs so //
NK079(dzu)003:1117: rnam par thar pa'i sgo gsum dang sbyar ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1118: phyag drug ni ye shes drug dang sbyar ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1119: zhabs drug ni ye shes drug /yul drug la ni
NK079(dzu)003:1120: mi dmigs pa'i tshul gyis mi 'gyur bar bstan te
NK079(dzu)003:1121: / bstan pa'i phyir rdo rje brag ces byas so //
NK079(dzu)003:1123: dge bcu'i las kyis grub pa la //
NK079(dzu)003:1125: dge ba bcu las 'das pa'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)003:1126: mnyam pa nyid la spyod pa'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:1127: de bzhin du khro bo khro mo 'og nas 'byung
NK079(dzu)003:1128: ba'i phyag mtshan rnams kyang tshul de ltar sbyar ro
NK079(dzu)003:1129: // shar lho mtshams su be con sngon po //
NK079(dzu)003:1133: g.yon dmar phyag g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis na /
NK079(dzu)003:1134: rdo rje dung chen khrag gis bkang nas bkrug cing gsol ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1135: bar ma gnyis na dbyug pa rin po che dang me spal bsnams /
NK079(dzu)003:1136: tha ma gnyis na sti ra'i dbyug pa dang khwa ta bsnams pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1137: zhabs drug me lha bardzisa pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1139: lho phyogs su gshin rje gshed po ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1141: dbu gsum la dbus sngon po /
NK079(dzu)003:1143: g.yon ljang nag /phyag g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis na /
NK079(dzu)003:1144: rdo rje dung chen khrag gis bskang nas dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1145: bar gnyis na dbyug pa mi mgo can dang dgra sta bsnams /
NK079(dzu)003:1146: tha ma gnyis na sti ra'i dbyug pa dang bya rog bsnams /
NK079(dzu)003:1147: zhabs drug gshin rje la bardzisa te bzhugs /
NK079(dzu)003:1148: lho nub mtshams su mi g.yo mgon po sku mdog ljang sngon /
NK079(dzu)003:1149: dbu gsum la dbus ljang sngon //
NK079(dzu)003:1151: g.yon smug nag /phyag g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis na //
NK079(dzu)003:1152: rdo rje dung chen khrag gis bskang nas bkrug cing gsol ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1153: bar ma gnyis na ral gri dar zhags bsnams /
NK079(dzu)003:1154: tha ma gnyis na sti ra'i dbyug pa dang 'ug pa bsnams /
NK079(dzu)003:1155: zhabs drug bden bral bardzisa pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1156: nub phyogs su ha ya g+r+ai ba //
NK079(dzu)003:1158: dbu gsum la dbus dmar g.yas dkar //
NK079(dzu)003:1161: rdo rje dung chen khrag gis bkang nas dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1162: bar ma gnyis na zhags pa dang spu gri bsnams pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1163: tha ma gnyis na sti ra'i dbyug pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1165: zhabs drug klu la bardzisa pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1166: nub byang gi mtshams na gzhan gyis mi thub sku mdog dmar skya /
NK079(dzu)003:1169: phyag dang po gnyis na rdo rje dung chen bkang ba dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1170: bar ma gnyis na ban d+ha dang rdul yab bsnams pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1171: tha ma gnyis na sti ra'i dbyug pa dang skrag bsnams pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1172: zhabs drug ber ma bardzisa pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1173: byang phyogs su bdud rtsi 'khyil pa sku mdog ljang nag /dbu gsum la dbus ljang /
NK079(dzu)003:1175: g.yon dud ka /phyag drug g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis na /
NK079(dzu)003:1176: rdo rje dung chen khrag gis bskang ba bkrug cing gsol ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1177: bar ma gnyis na dbyug to dang rgya gram bsnams pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1178: tha ma gnyis na sti ra'i dbyug pa dang pu shud bsnams /
NK079(dzu)003:1179: zhabs drug gnod sbyin bardzisa pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1180: byang shar mtshams su khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1182: dbu gsum la dbus ser po /
NK079(dzu)003:1185: phyag drug g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis na /
NK079(dzu)003:1186: rdo rje dung chen khrag gis bskang ba dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1187: bar ma gnyis na gzhu dang mda' bsnams /
NK079(dzu)003:1188: tha ma gnyis na sti ra'i dbyug pa dang srin bya bsnams /
NK079(dzu)003:1189: zhabs drug dbang ldan bardzisa pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1190: 'og gi phyogs su stobs po che sku mdog dud
NK079(dzu)003:1191: ka /dbu gsum la dbus dud ka /g.yas nag po
NK079(dzu)003:1193: phyag drug g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis na /
NK079(dzu)003:1194: rdo rje dung chen khrag gis bkang ba dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1195: bar ma gnyis tho ba dang zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1196: tha ma gnyis gshol dang gtun shing bsnams /
NK079(dzu)003:1198: steng gi phyogs su h'u ka ra sku mdog sngo skya /
NK079(dzu)003:1199: dbu gsum la dbus sngo skya /
NK079(dzu)003:1202: phyag drug g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis na rdo rje
NK079(dzu)003:1203: dung chen khrag gis bkang ba dkrug cing gsol ba
NK079(dzu)003:1204: / bar ma gnyis na mda' gzhu bsnams /
NK079(dzu)003:1205: tha ma gnyis na tho ba dang chu srin bsnams pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1206: zhabs drug nyi zla gza' skar bardzisa pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1207: de dag thams cad thod skam gyi dbu brgyan byas pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1208: thod rlon gyi phreng ba sha stag go //
NK079(dzu)003:1209: de'i pho nya bka' nyan ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1210: rdo rje phra men gtum bag can //
NK079(dzu)003:1211: 'jigs pa'i gzugs can mang po ste //
NK079(dzu)003:1212: de dag cir yang 'grub par byed //
NK079(dzu)003:1214: 'phra men ma stag gi mgo can dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1222: phag gi mgo can rnams te /
NK079(dzu)003:1223: de dag g.yas pa ni sti ra thogs nas za zhing rgyugs /
NK079(dzu)003:1224: g.yon pa ni cir yang 'gyur ba'i mtshon cha thogs nas /
NK079(dzu)003:1225: khro bo'i bka' bzhin las byed pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1226: gzhan du na rdo rje phra men ma ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1227: sems dang sems las byung ba'i chos lta bu ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1228: ye shes dang ye shes kyi byin rlabs las byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1229: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng ba las /
NK079(dzu)003:1230: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi le'u sta bcu
NK079(dzu)003:1231: gnyis pa'o ////da ni khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bshad de
NK079(dzu)003:1232: // rdo rje srin mo chen mo ni //
NK079(dzu)003:1233: 'jigs byed chen mor snang ba ste //
NK079(dzu)003:1234: phyag kyang srin po chen po ster //
NK079(dzu)003:1235: mthun te zhabs kyang de dang 'dra //
NK079(dzu)003:1237: khro mo rnams kyi sku dang phyag dang zhabs khro bo dang 'dra /
NK079(dzu)003:1238: mi mthun pa phyag g.yas par dril bu thogs //
NK079(dzu)003:1239: gzhan du na dril bu shes rab //
NK079(dzu)003:1242: dur mo rdo las me byung nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1243: brtsa la bsreg pa'i tshul du /
NK079(dzu)003:1244: pho nya pho dang pho nya mo byung nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1245: ci yang brlag par byed ces bya ba'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:1246: de la khro mo ni gtso mo ral gcig ma /
NK079(dzu)003:1247: shar phyogs su rdo rje snyems ma /
NK079(dzu)003:1248: de bzhin du rdo rjer sder mo /
NK079(dzu)003:1249: rdo rje dur khrod bdag mo /
NK079(dzu)003:1250: rdo rje gtun khung ma dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1255: rdo rje skul byed ma dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1257: rdo rje brjed byed ma dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1259: rdo rje bdud rtsi sbyor byed ma dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1261: nang gi pho nya bcu gnyis ni rdo rje rmangs byed ma dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1265: rdo rje rmugs byed ma dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1266: rdo rje srin mo snying za ma dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1267: rdo rje skul byed ma dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1268: rdo rje 'beb ma dpal bdag ma dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1270: rdo rje gnas ma mgyogs byed ma dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1271: rdo rje che bsgrub ma dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1273: 'di rnams kun kyang rin po che dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1274: rdo rje rgyu las byung ba'i gshogs pa gdengs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1275: dbu dang sku la sogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1278: chu srin gyi stod g.yogs dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1280: za byed kyi kha 'bar bas zhags pa kun gyi phyag na /
NK079(dzu)003:1281: sbod gtong rdo rje nam mkha' lding dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1285: kang ka'i lus la chu srin gyi mgo can //
NK079(dzu)003:1286: gshog sbub dang sbug sebs thams cad nas /
NK079(dzu)003:1287: lcags kyi rgyun btabs pa 'dra ba 'byung ba /
NK079(dzu)003:1288: sder mong thams cad rdo rje lcags kyu /
NK079(dzu)003:1289: mchu rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i bzong dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1292: rdo rje ka ma 'bud ka /rdo rje mching bar byed pa'i mchu dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1294: 'di lta bu phyag na bsnams so //
NK079(dzu)003:1295: gzhan du rnam par grol ba yi /
NK079(dzu)003:1296: skye mched bcu gnyis kyi yul gzhig ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1297: chos kyi dbyings su gyur pa la bya zhes /
NK079(dzu)003:1298: rtse gcig bsdus pa las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1299: pho nya 'phra men ma rnams te /
NK079(dzu)003:1303: pu shud kyi mgo can dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1305: pha bang gi mgo can dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1306: sre mong gi mgo can dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1308: smig bu'i mgo can rnams so //
NK079(dzu)003:1309: gzhan du na chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las 'byung zhes 'chad /
NK079(dzu)003:1311: rin chen me tog bor nas su //
NK079(dzu)003:1312: gang la bab pa'i lha de ni //
NK079(dzu)003:1313: nye bar 'grub pa the tshom med ces gsungs pa yin no //
NK079(dzu)003:1314: gong ma lta bu'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK079(dzu)003:1315: rin po che'i me tog bor te //
NK079(dzu)003:1316: gsang ba'i lha de bsgrubs nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1317: 'grub bo zhes bya ba'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:1319: chos kyi dbyings khro bo dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1320: khro mo'i tshul du snang ba la gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi rig pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1321: ye shes rig pa'i me tog bor ro zhes bya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1322: khro bo khro mo thams cad bdag tu tha mi dad pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1324: zhes rtse gcig bsdus pa las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1325: de nas slob ma'i dam tshig bstan te /
NK079(dzu)003:1326: dge dang mi dge'i chos rnams la //
NK079(dzu)003:1327: lhag par bstan par mi bya ste //
NK079(dzu)003:1328: mnyam nyid rig pa'i klong zhugs nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1329: ci la yang thogs pa med par spyad do //
NK079(dzu)003:1330: zhes bsgo bo zhes gsungs te /
NK079(dzu)003:1331: lhag par dge ba la gtsor sbyong ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1333: mi dge ba la gtsor spyod pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1334: sems can phal pa yin no //
NK079(dzu)003:1335: theg pa chen po'i chos thams cad kun rdzob tu khro bo khro mor mnyam la /
NK079(dzu)003:1336: don dam par skye 'gags med par mnyam pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1337: ci la yang thogs pa med par 'jug pa'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:1338: de nas 'khor dang bcas pa spyang drangs ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1339: de yi pho nya bka' nyan ni //
NK079(dzu)003:1340: rdo rje phra men gtum bag can //
NK079(dzu)003:1341: rdo rje dbyugs pa blangs nas su //
NK079(dzu)003:1342: g.yab mo sngas kyang g.yab par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:1343: de nas dkyil 'khor bzhugs par brtag /mchod pa chen po dbul bar bya //
NK079(dzu)003:1345: de la bdag gi lus la sngon gtso bo sh+r+ai he ru ka lus la khyab par bsdu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1346: h'u ka ra klad pa'i rgyab tu bsdu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1347: rnam par rgyal ba ni dpral bar bsdu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1348: ha ya g+r+ai ba ni kha nas thong ka'i bar tu bsdu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1349: khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba ni lag pa g.yas pa la bsdu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1350: be chen sngon po ni g.yon pa la bsdu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1351: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa snying gar bsdu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1352: ya man+ta ka ni lte bar bsdu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1353: gzhan gyi mi thub pa rkang g.yas pa la bsdu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1354: mi g.yo mgon po ni rkang pa g.yon pa la bsdu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1355: stobs po che gsang ba la bsdu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1357: dbus kyi gtso bo he ru ka'am /
NK079(dzu)003:1358: gang bsgom pa'i lhar bsgom mo //
NK079(dzu)003:1359: pho nya thams cad ba spu'i bu ga thams cad la bsdu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1360: srin mo rnams kyang tshur de ltar bsdu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1361: gzhan du na sems dang sems las byung ba'i chos gnas gyur pa la bya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1362: ye shes kyi byin rlabs las byung ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1363: chos kyi dbyings nyid de la /
NK079(dzu)003:1364: dbyings kyi ye shes kyis mnyam pa nyid du sbyor zhing dmigs par snyoms par 'jug pa'i tshe /
NK079(dzu)003:1365: sems dpa' gnas gyur pas ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1366: reg pa dang yid la byed pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1373: gnyid gnas gyur pa'i bar du slong zhing skul bar byed pa ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1374: chos kyi dbyings dang ye shes las byung nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1375: slar dbyings su 'dzud pas sems dpa' gnas 'gyur ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1376: 'phra men bskul ma zhes bya ste //
NK079(dzu)003:1377: gzhan reg pa la sogs pa snyoms par gyur pa'i gnas /
NK079(dzu)003:1378: gzhan gyis bsad pa'i god la 'brang ba'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:1379: bya rgod mgo can zhes bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1380: ri bo brtsegs pa las ni mgyogs pa'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)003:1381: bya rgod mgo can ces smos pa'i phyir ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1382: 'dun par gyur pa ni dbyings dang ye shes mnyam pa nyid du 'dod pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1384: bya rog gi mgo can no //
NK079(dzu)003:1385: yid la byed pa gnas gyur pa //
NK079(dzu)003:1386: dbyings dang ye shes mnyam pa nyid du shes pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1387: 'phra men nam 'grangs ma zhes bya ba ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1388: chos kyi dbyings ni nyal zhing ye shes phyir mi
NK079(dzu)003:1389: 'brang bas mtshan mo longs la nyin mo nyal bas
NK079(dzu)003:1391: mos par gyur pa'i dbyings dang ye shes mnyam par gyur pa 'dzin pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1393: khra'i mgo can no dran par gyur pa ni mnyam par gyur pa nyid la brjed pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1394: 'phra men ma bsgrim ma zhes bya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1395: pha wang gi mgo can no //
NK079(dzu)003:1396: 'byed par gyur pa ni mnyam pa nyid kyi nang
NK079(dzu)003:1397: du rdul tsam yang log par rtog pa mi gnas
NK079(dzu)003:1398: te / dper na mar khol ba'i nang du chu
NK079(dzu)003:1399: mi gnas pa dang 'dra bar sel cing skems pa'i
NK079(dzu)003:1400: te / phyir / 'phra men ma bsod ma zhes bya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1401: sre mong gi mgo can no //
NK079(dzu)003:1403: mnyam pa nyid las gzhan du mi g.yo pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1404: 'phra men ma sbad ma zhes bya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1406: dad pa gyur pa ni mnyam pa nyid du 'gro bas /
NK079(dzu)003:1407: 'phra men ma mgyogs ma zhes bya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1408: pu shud kyi mgo can no //
NK079(dzu)003:1409: gnyid gyur pa ni mnyam pa nyid gsal te /
NK079(dzu)003:1410: mnyam pa dang mi mthun pa'i rnams myos par byed pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1411: 'phra men ma myos byed ma zhes bya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1413: de rnams kyi las kyi skabs kyi bre brag la ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1414: 'phra men ma 'bros ma zhes bya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1416: ci'i phyir 'phra men ma bya zhe na /
NK079(dzu)003:1417: dbyings dang ye shes kyi dbyings kyi byin gyis brlabs pa ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1418: dbyings kyis byin gyis brlabs kyis ni de kun la byams /
NK079(dzu)003:1419: ye shes kyi byin gyi brlabs kyis ni dngos po kun zab pa'i phyir ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1420: de rnams kyi lus su grub pa dkyus nas smos pa nyid do //
NK079(dzu)003:1421: dbyings dang ye shes kyi lus dang yan lag go //
NK079(dzu)003:1423: ba spu'i bu ga nas 'byung ste 'phra men no //
NK079(dzu)003:1428: zangs kyi kha spu can dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1429: zangs kyi pags pa can la sogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1430: bye ba 'bum phrag dang brgya rtsa brgyad gcig 'byung ba yang /
NK079(dzu)003:1432: zhes gcig las 'phros pa'i tan tra las 'byung /
NK079(dzu)003:1433: se gol gtogs pa tsam gyis kyang //
NK079(dzu)003:1434: mgyogs mas phyogs bcu gar yang phyin //
NK079(dzu)003:1435: de la zhen nas 'gro byed pa //
NK079(dzu)003:1436: bya rog mgo can yin pa kun //
NK079(dzu)003:1438: gang la bya ba'i skabs kyis mgyogs ma dang zab
NK079(dzu)003:1439: mo la sogs pa zhon te 'gro na 'grub ba'i
NK079(dzu)003:1440: don to // gzhan du mgyogs ma nyid chos kyi dbyings kyis byin gyis brlabs las /
NK079(dzu)003:1441: dbyings kyi kun la khyab pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1442: 'gro ba med par phyin pa'o zhes /
NK079(dzu)003:1443: dpal 'phreng dkar po las bshad de //
NK079(dzu)003:1444: sbed byed mas ni sbas pa na //
NK079(dzu)003:1445: mthu chen lha srin gang gis kyang //
NK079(dzu)003:1446: de la mthong bar mi nus na //
NK079(dzu)003:1447: gzhan gyis mthong bar ga la nus //
NK079(dzu)003:1448: gzhan du na sbad byed ma ni //
NK079(dzu)003:1449: chos kyi dbyings mi dmigs pa'i byin rlabs yin pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1451: so so'i gnas su spyan drangs te //
NK079(dzu)003:1452: dmar chen arga gsol nas kyang //
NK079(dzu)003:1453: mchod yon gzhan yang dbul bar bya //
NK079(dzu)003:1454: rdo rje dbyangs kyi bstod byas te /
NK079(dzu)003:1455: de nas las rnams bsgrub par bya zhes gsungs te /
NK079(dzu)003:1456: sha chen dang ba zha la sogs pa sman sna lnga dang sbyar te /
NK079(dzu)003:1457: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas pas //
NK079(dzu)003:1459: khros pas yud las brlag mdzad de //
NK079(dzu)003:1460: rlag par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK079(dzu)003:1462: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1463: las kyi le'u ste bcu bdun pa'o ////da ni drag po'i las rnams bshad par bya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1464: rdo rje 'phra men sbyor ba yi //
NK079(dzu)003:1465: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir bkug nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1466: stod pa'i tshul du rab bstabs nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1467: lha yang rung ste rlag par 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)003:1469: 'phra men ma stag gi mgo can la sogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1471: gang la bya ba yud tsam gyis /
NK079(dzu)003:1473: khro bo dang khro mo'i zhal du bstabs te //
NK079(dzu)003:1474: bstod pa'i tshul du gsol bar bsgoms nas /
NK079(dzu)003:1475: lam rgyud drug gi sems can gang yang rung ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1477: gzhan du na chos kyi dbyings dang //
NK079(dzu)003:1478: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes lnga'i byin rlabs //
NK079(dzu)003:1479: rnam par grol ba'i skye mched bcu gcig gis //
NK079(dzu)003:1480: lam rgyud lnga'i sems can dngos por lta ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1481: stong pa nyid dam tshig las 'gal bas /
NK079(dzu)003:1482: de dag rang bzhin gyi za bar 'gyur zhes tan tra karma ma le las bshad to //
NK079(dzu)003:1483: 'ug pa'i mgo can la sogs pa'i //
NK079(dzu)003:1485: mig dang rna ba sna dang lce //
NK079(dzu)003:1486: de bas mchog bsgom nyams par 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)003:1488: khyung dang kha la sogs bya rgod mgo can la sogs pa khrag 'thung btang ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1489: gang la bya ba'i dbang po 'byin par bsgoms na /
NK079(dzu)003:1490: de'i dbang po nyams nas de'i mig long ba dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1495: gzhan du na stong pa nyid kyi ye shes drug gi byin rlabs kyis /
NK079(dzu)003:1496: ril por lta ba'i dngos po rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:1497: yang dag pa nyid las 'gal ba'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:1498: rang bzhin gyis mnyam par byed ces tan tra karma ma le las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1499: 'phra men rnams ni sbad bya ste //
NK079(dzu)003:1500: de'i bsgrub pa rab gcad cing //
NK079(dzu)003:1501: gsang ste 'khrugs par bsgoms byas nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1505: gang la bya ba'i las thams cad mi 'grub par gegs byed pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1506: gsang sde thams cad 'byed pa'i dkrugs ma byed pa bsgoms na /
NK079(dzu)003:1507: don du gnyer ba mi 'grub cing gsang sde gcig gcig shar te gnyer te 'byed par 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1508: gzhan du na stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi byin brlabs kyis /
NK079(dzu)003:1509: dngos po la gtso bor bsgrub pa byed pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1510: tshig gi sgra la gtsor byas te //
NK079(dzu)003:1511: phyogs gcig tu byed pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1512: stong pa nyid las 'gal ba'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)003:1513: don du bsgrub pa mi 'grub cing //
NK079(dzu)003:1514: gsang ste yang byed bar 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1515: zhes karma ma le las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1516: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1517: drag po'i las kyi le'u ste bco brgyad pa'o ////da ni drag po'i hom gyi las bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:1518: hom khung zur gsum gdengs pa la //
NK079(dzu)003:1519: rdo rje mda' gzhu ldan byas te //
NK079(dzu)003:1520: thod pa dag gis rnam par brgyan //
NK079(dzu)003:1521: spyan drangs sregs na lha yang 'chi //
NK079(dzu)003:1523: thabs khung zur gsum du byas la //
NK079(dzu)003:1524: gwa mda' gzhu rnam par bkang nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1526: tha ma phur pa nag po gsum btab la /
NK079(dzu)003:1527: lcags thag gam thag pa nag pos bskor te /
NK079(dzu)003:1528: khro bo dang khro mo dang 'phra men ma rnams spyan drangs te /
NK079(dzu)003:1529: tsher ma'i shing las me sbar nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1530: tsh+wa ba'i me dang lan tsh+wa dang //
NK079(dzu)003:1531: dug dang mi khrag ra'i khrag /skye tshe ldong ros lcags phya las //
NK079(dzu)003:1532: khro bo khro mo 'phra men gyi //
NK079(dzu)003:1533: gsang sngags rnams ni bzlas nas su //
NK079(dzu)003:1534: gang la bya ba'i gzugs dag ni //
NK079(dzu)003:1536: 'phra men mngags te bkug nas ni //
NK079(dzu)003:1537: thab khung bsregs na mod la 'chi //
NK079(dzu)003:1538: gsur dang bsregs pa'i sha rnams kyis //
NK079(dzu)003:1539: lha rnams thams cad mchod par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:1540: rdo rje'i glu ni blangs nas su //
NK079(dzu)003:1541: 'byung po'i sha ni shim tu zhim //
NK079(dzu)003:1542: 'byung po'i khrag ni shin tu zhim //
NK079(dzu)003:1543: 'byung po'i rus pa zhim pa ste //
NK079(dzu)003:1544: gsol te thams cad dgyes par mdzad //
NK079(dzu)003:1548: gzhan du sku gsung thugs kyi ye shes kyi mes
NK079(dzu)003:1549: sku gsung thugs dang mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad
NK079(dzu)003:1550: bsregs pa dang / ye shes kyis byin gyis brlabs kyis mda' 'phang pa ltar /
NK079(dzu)003:1552: sku gsung thugs dang mthun par gyur pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1553: khro bo dang khro mo'i rang bzhin gyis mnyes pa yin zhing /
NK079(dzu)003:1554: de ltar go ba ni glu dbyangs blangs shing ri bo brtsegs pa'i /
NK079(dzu)003:1556: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng ba las /
NK079(dzu)003:1557: drag po'i hom gyi le'u ste bcu dgu pa'o ////da ni drag po'i phur pa'i las bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:1558: lcags sam nag po'i shing rnams la //
NK079(dzu)003:1559: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zur gsum //
NK079(dzu)003:1560: khro bo khro mo rnams bsgoms te //
NK079(dzu)003:1561: btab te lha yang rlag par 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)003:1563: lcags sam shing nag po kha dog can la phur pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1564: rgya mdud rtse zur gsum du gzhogs te /
NK079(dzu)003:1565: rgya mdud kyi steng du h'u ka ra dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1566: ral pa gcig ma dngos su go rim bzhin du /
NK079(dzu)003:1567: khro bo khro mo rnams bsgoms te //
NK079(dzu)003:1568: gang la bya ba'i gzugs dang ming rus la btab na /
NK079(dzu)003:1569: lha yang gzer thabs dang rim gyis btab ste //
NK079(dzu)003:1571: ri rab dang gling bzhi'i ngos la sogs pa la bris te btab na /
NK079(dzu)003:1572: phur pa gcig gis phyogs bcur btab par 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1573: gzhan du na gnyis su med pa'i ye shes stong pa nyid kyis byin rlabs /
NK079(dzu)003:1574: khro bo dang khro mo yin la //
NK079(dzu)003:1575: des ma khyab pa med de /
NK079(dzu)003:1576: sems kyi phur pa gcig btab pas //
NK079(dzu)003:1577: phyogs bcur btab par 'gyur zhes gu h+ya til ka dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1578: ki la ya bcu gnyis kyis tan tra las byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1579: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1580: drag po'i phur pa'i le'u ste nyi shu pa'o ////drag po'i gtor ma bshad do //
NK079(dzu)003:1581: lcags dag dang ni rdo rje dag /khrag las sprul te bsreg pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1583: sbyar ba dag /sbyar bas gtor na de rlag 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)003:1585: lcags phye dang rdo rje dug rnams mi 'am khyi'am ra'i khrag la sbrus te /
NK079(dzu)003:1587: 'bru nag po tsan dan dang sbyar te /
NK079(dzu)003:1588: gang la bya ba bkug te byin na /
NK079(dzu)003:1589: mthong bas khrag tu skyugs rul nas 'chi bar 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1590: gzhan du na stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis kun la khyab pa'i phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:1591: de nyid bsgoms pas rang bzhin shing rul bar 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1592: zhes sgyu 'phrul dra ba las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1593: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+ma mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1594: drag po'i gtor ma'i le'u ste nyi shu gcig pa'o ////da ni drag po'i sbyor ba'i las bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:1595: khro bo khro mo'i dkyil 'khor gtum chen du /
NK079(dzu)003:1596: kho bo'i tho bas brdung ba yi //
NK079(dzu)003:1597: rdo rje'i gtun phrug bsgoms byas nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1598: lha yang rung ste rlag par 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)003:1600: khro mo rnams kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK079(dzu)003:1601: khro bo rnams kyis brdung bar bsgoms na //
NK079(dzu)003:1602: gang yang rung te brdungs par 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1603: gzhan du na khro mo'i lta bu chos kyi dbyings nyid ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1604: 'jig rten thams cad khyab pa'i gtun no //
NK079(dzu)003:1605: khro bo lta bu dbyings nyid rig pa ni //
NK079(dzu)003:1606: 'jig rten thams cad la brdungs pa'i tho ba zhes /
NK079(dzu)003:1607: thabs kyi phreng ba'i gtan tra las byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1608: gzhan gyis drag po'i sbyor ba zhig byas na yang /
NK079(dzu)003:1609: las 'di rnams kyi byed pa nyid la slar bzlog par 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1610: drag po'i las byed pa'i tshe /
NK079(dzu)003:1611: chas gos nag po rnam pa lnga dang ldan par bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1612: drag po'i las rnams bshad zin no //
NK079(dzu)003:1613: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo'i phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1614: drag po'i las kyi le'u ste nyi shu gnyis pa'o ////da ni gnas btab pa'i cho ga bya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1615: drag po'i las kyis sgro ba'i rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:1616: 'khor ba lam lnga'i sgo bcad nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1617: rnam shes h'u gis bsdu rdung nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1618: 'og min gnas mchog bla na med //
NK079(dzu)003:1619: gtso bo lnga'am gtso mo lnga //
NK079(dzu)003:1620: sems dpa' dang ni sems ma dang //
NK079(dzu)003:1621: khro bo dang ni khro mo rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:1622: sbyor ba'i lhums su phata kyis 'phang //
NK079(dzu)003:1624: drag po'i las kyis bsgral ba'i rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:1626: sngags 'bru lngas sgo bcad par bsgoms nas /
NK079(dzu)003:1627: rnam par shes pa h'u gis bsdus nas /
NK079(dzu)003:1629: 'og min gyi gnas na lha gong na smos pa'i rnal 'byor pa mdzad pa'i lhums su /
