NK079(dzu)003:1631: nges par 'grub pa zhes tan tra du ma las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1632: tan tra snying rje rol pa las kyang 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1633: gzhan du na chos kyi dbyings mnyam pa nyid la snyoms par zhugs pa'i tshe /
NK079(dzu)003:1634: sems can dmyal bar lta ba'i rgyu ni zhe sdang
NK079(dzu)003:1635: la dngos po yod par blta ba ni yin te
NK079(dzu)003:1636: / zhe sdang la rang bzhin med par shes shing //
NK079(dzu)003:1637: zhe sdang gi sems mi skye bas na /
NK079(dzu)003:1638: dmyal ba'i sgo gcad pa yin no //
NK079(dzu)003:1639: de bzhin du yang 'dod chags dang gti mug la rang bzhin med par shes shing /
NK079(dzu)003:1640: de dag gi sems mi skye bas na /
NK079(dzu)003:1641: yi dwags byol song gi sgo yang gcad pa yin no //
NK079(dzu)003:1642: lha dang mir skye ba'i rgyu ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1643: dge ba bcu dang bsam gtan bzhi dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1644: snyoms par 'jug pa bzhi bsgrub pa yin no //
NK079(dzu)003:1645: de dag rang bzhin med par rig pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1646: sems mi skye ba ni lha dang mi sgo gcod pa yin no //
NK079(dzu)003:1647: bdag gi lto zhes bya ba ni chos kyi dbyings te /
NK079(dzu)003:1648: bla na med pa'i phyir 'og ma ni gnas zhes bya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1649: chos kyi dbyings nyid rig pa'i tshe //
NK079(dzu)003:1650: lha dang lha mo'i tshul 'brel bar rig pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1651: de nyid byang chub kyi sems yin pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1652: rang gi rnam par shes pa der 'byor par sgoms na nges par 'grub bo //
NK079(dzu)003:1653: dper na rgyal po ra ma nas bsad pa thams
NK079(dzu)003:1654: cad lhar skye bar 'gyur bar smon lam btab pas
NK079(dzu)003:1655: / de bzhin du sngar nas gsod pa lhar 'grub
NK079(dzu)003:1656: bo zhes drang srong mngon par shes pa can gyis
NK079(dzu)003:1657: / bshad pa ste / 'di ltar chos kyi dbyings la snyoms par sbyor ba lta ci smos te /
NK079(dzu)003:1658: snying rje rol pa'i tan tra las byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1659: gnas bstab pa'i cho ga bshad zin to //
NK079(dzu)003:1660: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1661: gnas bstab pa'i le'u ste nyi shu gsum pa'o ////da ni dbang gi las bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:1662: zla gam dkyil 'khor rtsibs brgyad par //
NK079(dzu)003:1663: khro bo khro mo spyan drangs te //
NK079(dzu)003:1664: mchod pa'i glu la sogs pas mchod //
NK079(dzu)003:1665: de nas las rnams brtsam par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:1668: lha rnams go rim bzhin spyan drangs te /
NK079(dzu)003:1669: de nas glu gar dang arga la sogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1670: yo byad dmar pos mchod par bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1671: chags pa'i rdo rje 'khor bcas pa //
NK079(dzu)003:1673: chugs pas yud la dbang mdzad de //
NK079(dzu)003:1674: dbang du ma gyur gang yang med //
NK079(dzu)003:1676: de nas chas gos rnams lnga yang ldan par bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1678: rdo rje 'phra men mngag nas su //
NK079(dzu)003:1679: bkug nas khro bo chen po yis //
NK079(dzu)003:1680: chags pa'i tshul gyis de lus la //
NK079(dzu)003:1681: dpal dang gzi brjid bsdus nas 'grub //
NK079(dzu)003:1683: rdo rje 'phra men ma rnams mngag nas /
NK079(dzu)003:1684: gang du bya ba de bkug pa ste //
NK079(dzu)003:1685: de'i lus dang nga ga dang sems dang dpal dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1687: ci yang nyan par bsgoms na /
NK079(dzu)003:1690: lus la grib ma 'khor ba dang 'dra bar //
NK079(dzu)003:1691: bdag la 'khor zhing rig mi mthun pa zhig na yang /
NK079(dzu)003:1692: lus ston cing ci bsgo ba bran bzhin byed de /
NK079(dzu)003:1693: ci sems la yang smra na /
NK079(dzu)003:1694: gzhan lta ci smos te 'grub pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1695: gzhan du na stong pa nyid kyi chos kyi dbyings kyis /
NK079(dzu)003:1696: phyi nang gi dngos po thams cad la khyab pas tha mi dad pa chags pa yin /
NK079(dzu)003:1697: de ltar chags pa'i rig pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK079(dzu)003:1698: phyogs bcu'i snod bcud kyi 'jig rten thams cad //
NK079(dzu)003:1699: bdag dang tha dad par rig pas //
NK079(dzu)003:1700: rang bzhin gyis byams shing 'khor ba yin te //
NK079(dzu)003:1701: bran bzhin byed pa yang bdag dang tha mi dad pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1702: thams cad bdag yin pas phyir /
NK079(dzu)003:1703: bdag nyid chen po zhes kyang de'i phyir bya //
NK079(dzu)003:1704: rnam gcig tu thams cad bdag gis sprul pa yin zhes bya /
NK079(dzu)003:1705: dbang chen bsdus pa'i tan tra las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1706: 'phra men ma rnams ni mngags so //
NK079(dzu)003:1707: de'i mig rna ba sna dang lce //
NK079(dzu)003:1708: lus dang sems bsgyur rnams bsgoms nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1709: kun la mdzes shing dga' bar 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)003:1711: rdo rje 'phra men ma rnams mngags te /
NK079(dzu)003:1712: de'i mig dang rna ba dang sna dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1714: bdag gis nyes pa byas na yang //
NK079(dzu)003:1717: de bzhin du 'grub ces bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:1718: gzhan du na stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis
NK079(dzu)003:1719: kun la khyab pas bdag dang tha mi dad par
NK079(dzu)003:1721: dbang po la khyab par 'gyur ba yin te /
NK079(dzu)003:1722: dper na bla bcol mkhan gyis mi rig pa zhig byas na yang /
NK079(dzu)003:1723: kun dga' bar gyur te rgod pa lta bu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1724: zhes ri bo brtsegs pa las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1725: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1726: dbang gi las bstan pa'i le'u ste nyi shu bzhi
NK079(dzu)003:1727: pa'o ////da ni dbang gi hom bshad par bya ste
NK079(dzu)003:1728: / hom khung zla gam gdengs pa las //
NK079(dzu)003:1729: rdo rje zhags pas brgyan par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:1730: de nas lha rnams spyan drangs te //
NK079(dzu)003:1734: rdo rje zhags pas brgyan te /
NK079(dzu)003:1735: kha dog dmar po phur pa btab ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1736: mtha' thag pa dmar pos bskor te /
NK079(dzu)003:1737: shing dri ma mnam pa la me sbar nas /
NK079(dzu)003:1738: zangs phye dang bu ram dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1740: gang la bya ba'i snying po rgya skyegs kyis bris
NK079(dzu)003:1741: te bsreg cing rdo rje 'phra men mas bdag la
NK079(dzu)003:1742: mi phan zhing / mi 'dza' ba'i sems pa'i rtog pa bsreg par bsgoms na /
NK079(dzu)003:1743: ci bsgo ba nyan cing phan par sems par 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1744: gzhan du na rnam par rtog pa ni bdag tu lta ba las 'byung ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1745: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi mes /
NK079(dzu)003:1746: bdag tu lta ba dngos por zhen nas rnam par
NK079(dzu)003:1747: rtog pa ni 'khor ba'i rgyu chen po yin pas
NK079(dzu)003:1748: / mi phan pa zhes bya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1749: bdag med pa'i ye shes rig nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1750: 'khor ba dang bral bas sems zhes bya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1751: de ltar rig nas bdag dang gzhan du tha mi dad pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1752: gzhan yang rang bzhin gyis 'jam zhing sems par 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1753: zhes glang po che las bshad do //
NK079(dzu)003:1754: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1755: dbang gi hom gyi le'u ste nyi shu lnga pa'o ////da ni dbang gi phur pa'i las bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:1756: zangs sam kha dog dmar po yi //
NK079(dzu)003:1757: shing la rgya mdud rtse zla gam //
NK079(dzu)003:1758: mgo la rgya mdud rtse zla gam //
NK079(dzu)003:1759: mgo la khro bo khro mor bsgoms te /
NK079(dzu)003:1762: zangs sam kha dog dmar po'i shing la /
NK079(dzu)003:1763: phur pa mgo rgya mdud la rtse zla gam du gzhogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1764: rgya mdud gyi steng dang ngos su khro bo khro mo rnams bsgoms te /
NK079(dzu)003:1765: gang dbang du bya ba'i de'i gzugs sam /
NK079(dzu)003:1766: ming rus bris pa la btab ste //
NK079(dzu)003:1767: bka' bzhin du byed par bsgoms na //
NK079(dzu)003:1769: ri rab gleng gzhi la sogs pa bris te btab na /
NK079(dzu)003:1774: gzhan du na chos kyi dbyings kyis //
NK079(dzu)003:1775: phyogs bcu thams cad du khyab la //
NK079(dzu)003:1776: de ltar rig pa'i ye shes ni phur pa yin te /
NK079(dzu)003:1777: thams cad du btab par 'gyur zhing //
NK079(dzu)003:1778: bdag dang tha mi dad par las thams cad rang bzhin gyis dbang du 'gyur ba yin no //
NK079(dzu)003:1779: zhes phur pa bcu gnyis kyi rgyud phyi ma las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1780: dbang gi phur pa bshad zin to //
NK079(dzu)003:1781: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1782: dbang gi phur pa bstan pa'i le'u ste nyi shu
NK079(dzu)003:1783: drug pa'o ////da ni dbang gi gtor ma bshad de
NK079(dzu)003:1784: / zangs phye dang ni bu ram dang //
NK079(dzu)003:1785: dmar po'i 'bras chan la sogs pa //
NK079(dzu)003:1786: sbyar bas gtor ma gtong bar bya //
NK079(dzu)003:1787: mthong bas nges par dbang du 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)003:1789: zangs phye dang 'bras dmar po'i chan la sogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1790: 'bru kha dog dmar po'i chan dang //
NK079(dzu)003:1791: bu ram chu la sogs pa la sbyar te /
NK079(dzu)003:1793: gang du bya ba bkug ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1794: phyis nas mthong bas de dbang du 'gyur te /
NK079(dzu)003:1796: ci bsgo ba yang nyan cing dbang du 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1797: gzhan du na chos kyi dbyings mtshan nyid med pas thams cad du khyab ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1798: bdag nyid chen po dang tha dad pas rang bzhin gyis dbang du 'gyur te /
NK079(dzu)003:1799: de ltar rig pa'i ye shes ni //
NK079(dzu)003:1800: gtor ma btang ba yin no zhes thabs kyi zhags pa'i rgyud phyi ma gnyis las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1801: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1802: dbang gi gtor ma'i le'u ste nyi shu bdun pa'o ////da ni sbyor ba'i las bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:1803: khro mo rnams kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK079(dzu)003:1804: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bsgoms byas nas //
NK079(dzu)003:1805: lha yang rung ste dbang du 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)003:1806: da ni bde ba chen po yin //
NK079(dzu)003:1808: khro mo'i dkyil 'khor du khro bo'i dkyil 'khor sbyor ba'i las kyis /
NK079(dzu)003:1809: lha man chad gang yang rung ste //
NK079(dzu)003:1810: thams cad dga' zhing dbang du 'gyur bar bsgoms nas /
NK079(dzu)003:1812: gzhan du na chos kyi dbyings mtshan nyid med pa kun la khyab pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1813: de ltar rig pa'i ye shes kyis ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1815: de ltar 'byor cig pa nyid ma nor bar rig pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1816: byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ste //
NK079(dzu)003:1817: de ni bde ba chen po'i dbang ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1818: kun tu khyab par rig pa ni //
NK079(dzu)003:1819: rang bzhin gyis dbang du 'gyur ro zhes /
NK079(dzu)003:1820: dbang chen bsdus pa'i tan tra las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1821: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1822: dbang 'byor pa'i le'u ste nyi shu brgyad pa'o ////da ni rgyas pa'i las bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:1823: gru bzhi'i dkyil 'khor rtsibs brgyad par //
NK079(dzu)003:1824: lha rnams 'khor bcas spyan drangs te //
NK079(dzu)003:1825: mchod pa glu la sogs pas mchod //
NK079(dzu)003:1826: de nas las rnams brtsam par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:1828: rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor du lha 'khor dang bcas pa spyan drangs te /
NK079(dzu)003:1829: yo byad ser por byas la /
NK079(dzu)003:1830: nga rgyal rdo rje 'khor bcas pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1832: dpal dang gzi brjid chen po rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:1833: yud tsam gyis ni rgyas mdzad de //
NK079(dzu)003:1835: de nas chas gos rnam pa lnga dang ldan par bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1836: khro bo khro mo 'khor bcas yang //
NK079(dzu)003:1837: rdo rje phra men 'khor bcas pas //
NK079(dzu)003:1838: dpal dang gzi brjid 'phel bsgoms na //
NK079(dzu)003:1839: bdag nyid chen por der 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1841: lha rnams kyis bdag gis dpal dang gzi brjid 'phel bar bsgoms na /
NK079(dzu)003:1842: nges par de bzhin du 'grub pa 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1844: gzhan du na chos nyid kyi dbyings nyid med pas //
NK079(dzu)003:1845: phyi nang gi dngos po thams cad la khyab ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1846: de ltar rig pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK079(dzu)003:1847: snod dang bcud kyi 'jig rten thams cad dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1848: bdag tu tha mi dad pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1850: bsod nams dang spyod pa thams cad la sogs pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1851: bdag yin pa'am bdag gi yin par bsgoms nas /
NK079(dzu)003:1852: dper na nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bar snang la shar ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1853: nyi ma'i rang bzhin dro ba yin pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1854: gzhan du dro ba yang nyi ma yin pa'am /
NK079(dzu)003:1855: yang na nyi ma'i 'od yin pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1856: nyi ma yin pa dang 'dra bas thams cad bdag gam /
NK079(dzu)003:1858: de'i phyir bdag nyid chen po yin ces dpal 'phreng dkar po las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1859: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las rgyas pa'i le'u
NK079(dzu)003:1860: ste nyi shu dgu pa'o ////da ni rgyas pa'i hom
NK079(dzu)003:1861: bshad do // hom khung gru bzhi gdengs pa la //
NK079(dzu)003:1862: rdo rje 'khor lo brgyan par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:1863: de nas lha rnams spyan drangs te //
NK079(dzu)003:1864: bsreg pas mchod cing dpal 'phel bsgom //
NK079(dzu)003:1866: hom khung gru bzhi la rdo rje 'khor los brgyan par bris te /
NK079(dzu)003:1867: phur pa kha dog ser po bzhi btab la /
NK079(dzu)003:1868: mthar thag pa ser pos bskor te //
NK079(dzu)003:1869: de nas lha rnams spyan drangs te //
NK079(dzu)003:1870: rin po che sna drangs te /
NK079(dzu)003:1871: rin po che sna lnga dang /
NK079(dzu)003:1873: mar khu la sogs pas bsreg shing mchod na /
NK079(dzu)003:1874: bdag gi dpal la sogs pa 'phel bar bsgoms na /
NK079(dzu)003:1877: gzhan du na chos kyi dbyings la //
NK079(dzu)003:1878: me long lta bu'i ye shes dmigs pa'i dus gcig na /
NK079(dzu)003:1879: gtso bo lnga dang gtso mo lnga'i sku lta bur byung /
NK079(dzu)003:1880: sems dpa' bcu drug dang sems ma bcu drug ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1882: de'i dbu rgyan lnga lnga ni dpe byad du byung ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1883: spyir ye shes kyi dngos po bsregs shing /
NK079(dzu)003:1884: rang bzhin gyis brgyan par 'gyur la //
NK079(dzu)003:1885: nyan thos las khyad par che ba'i phyir ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1886: dpal 'phel zhing bya ba thabs kyi zhags pa las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1887: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1888: rgyas pa'i hom gyi le'u ste sum cu pa'o ////da ni rgyas pa'i phur ba'i las bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:1889: gser ram ser ba'i shing rnams la //
NK079(dzu)003:1890: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zur bzhi //
NK079(dzu)003:1891: lha rnams bsgoms te gdab par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:1892: 'di ni rgyas pa'i las la shis //
NK079(dzu)003:1894: gser ram ser po'i shing rnams la /
NK079(dzu)003:1895: mgo bo rgya mdud zur bzhi par bzhog ste /
NK079(dzu)003:1896: rgya mdud la lha rnams bkod de /
NK079(dzu)003:1897: gdab na gang la bya ba de la btab na 'grub cing /
NK079(dzu)003:1898: dpal dang gzi brjid rgyas par 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1899: gzhan du na chos kyi dbyings la longs spyod rdzogs pa 'byung /
NK079(dzu)003:1900: longs spyod rdzogs par 'byung bar nya da //
NK079(dzu)003:1901: ting nge 'dzin phur pa yin pas //
NK079(dzu)003:1902: rang bzhin gyi dpal dang gzi brjid rgyas pa yin no //
NK079(dzu)003:1903: zhes tan tra du ma las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1904: thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1905: rgyas pa'i phur pa'i le'u ste sum cu gcig pa'o ////da ni rgyas pa'i gtor ma bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:1906: gser phye 'bras chan ser po rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:1907: 'o ma sbrang rtsi gtor ma ni //
NK079(dzu)003:1908: rgyas par 'gyur ba'i gtor ma ste //
NK079(dzu)003:1909: gtan na thams cad rgyas par 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)003:1911: gser phye dang 'bras ser po'i chan la sogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:1912: 'o ma dang sbrang rtsir sbyar te //
NK079(dzu)003:1913: btang na dpal dang gzi brjid rgyas shing 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1914: gzhan du na chos kyi dbyings mtshan nyid med pa thams cad la khyab te /
NK079(dzu)003:1915: bdag nyid chen po dang tha mi dad pa rang bzhin gyis thams cad rgyas par 'gyur te /
NK079(dzu)003:1916: de ltar rig pa'i ye shes ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1917: byin cing gtang ba yin ces /
NK079(dzu)003:1919: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1920: rgyas pa'i gtor ma'i le'u ste sum cu gnyis pa'o ////da ni rgyas pa'i sbyor ba'i las bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:1921: lha mo rnams kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK079(dzu)003:1923: byang chub sems ni spro bsgoms na //
NK079(dzu)003:1924: de yis rgyas pa'i las 'grub bo //
NK079(dzu)003:1926: lha mo rnams dang lha sbyor ba chen po mdzad cing /
NK079(dzu)003:1927: bde ba chen pos rol cing longs spyod rgyas par bsgoms nas /
NK079(dzu)003:1929: gzhan du na ting nge 'dzin dkyil 'khor ni /
NK079(dzu)003:1930: lha dang lha mo'i tshul du sbyor la /
NK079(dzu)003:1932: byang chub kyi sems spros pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1933: longs spyod chen po rgyas pa yin zhes /
NK079(dzu)003:1934: ri bo brtsegs pa las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1935: rgyas pa'i las bshad zin to //
NK079(dzu)003:1936: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1937: rgyas pa'i sbyor ba'i le'u ste sum cu gsum pa'o ////da ni zhi ba'i las bshad de //
NK079(dzu)003:1938: zlum po'i dkyil 'khor rtsibs brgyad par //
NK079(dzu)003:1939: lha rnams 'khor bcas sbyan drangs te //
NK079(dzu)003:1940: dkar po'i yon gyis mchod par byed //
NK079(dzu)003:1941: de nas las rnams brtsams par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:1945: yo byad dkar po dang dbyangs la sogs pas /
NK079(dzu)003:1947: zhi ba'i las brtsams zhes bya ba'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:1948: gti mug rdo rje 'khor bcas pas //
NK079(dzu)003:1950: yud tsam nyid la zhi mdzad de //
NK079(dzu)003:1951: zhi bar grub la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:1953: chas gos rnam pa gsum dang ldan par byas de las bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1954: lha rnams 'khor bcas thams cad kyis //
NK079(dzu)003:1955: 'khrugs pa thams cad zhi mdzad par //
NK079(dzu)003:1956: bsgoms na thams cad yud tsam gyis //
NK079(dzu)003:1957: zhi bar gyur te the tshom med //
NK079(dzu)003:1959: lha dang lha mo 'khor dang bcas pa 'khrugs pa la sogs te /
NK079(dzu)003:1960: gnod sdig thams cad zhi bar bsgom na de bzhin du 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1961: gzhan du na chos kyi dbyings stong pa nyid kyi ye shes zhi ba'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK079(dzu)003:1962: thams cad du khyab pas thams cad du zhi bar 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1963: gzhan las kyi 'phreng ba las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1964: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng ba las /
NK079(dzu)003:1965: zhi ba'i las kyi le'u ste sum cu bzhi pa'o ////da ni zhi ba'i hmo bshad de //
NK079(dzu)003:1966: hom khung zlum po gdengs pa las //
NK079(dzu)003:1967: rdo rje pad+ma rgyas par bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:1968: phur pa dkar po drug btab ste //
NK079(dzu)003:1969: spyan drangs dngul phye la sogs mchod //
NK079(dzu)003:1971: hom khung zlum po gdeng pa las /
NK079(dzu)003:1972: lha gong ma 'khor dang bcas pa spyan drangs te /
NK079(dzu)003:1973: yo byad dkar pos sreg cing mchod de /
NK079(dzu)003:1974: 'khrug pa la sogs pa thams cad zhi bar bsgoms na /
NK079(dzu)003:1975: gzhan du chos nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK079(dzu)003:1976: rnam par rtog pa la sogs pa 'khrugs pa thams cad rang bzhin gyis zhi zhing /
NK079(dzu)003:1977: lha rnams kyang mchod par 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:1979: tan tra glang po chur zhugs pa las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1980: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo 'phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:1981: zhi ba'i hmo gyi le'u ste sum cu lnga pa'o ////da ni zhi ba'i phur pa las bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:1982: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse bzlum po //
NK079(dzu)003:1983: lha rnams bsgoms te btab par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:1984: 'di ni zhi ba'i las la shis //
NK079(dzu)003:1986: rngul lam shing mdog dkar po las //
NK079(dzu)003:1987: phur pa rgya mdud zlum por gzhog la /
NK079(dzu)003:1988: rgya mdud la lha rnams bkod de //
NK079(dzu)003:1989: zhi bar bsgoms te btab na /
NK079(dzu)003:1991: gzhan du na chos nyid ma nor bar rig pa nyid ting nge 'dzin gyi phur pa yin te /
NK079(dzu)003:1992: thams cad rang bzhin gyis zhi bar 'gyur zhes rtse gcig bsdus pa las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:1993: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng ba las /
NK079(dzu)003:1994: zhi ba'i phur pa'i le'u ste sum cu drug pa'o ////da ni zhi ba'i gtor ma bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:1995: dngul lam 'bras chan dkar po rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:1996: 'o mar sbyar ba'i gtor ma ni //
NK079(dzu)003:1997: zhi bar 'gyur ba'i gtor ma te //
NK079(dzu)003:1998: mkhas pas zhi bar bsgoms zhing gtor //
NK079(dzu)003:2000: dngul dang 'bru dkar po'i chan la sogs pa /
NK079(dzu)003:2002: gtor na lha man chad 'chi bar 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:2003: gzhan du na chos thams cad kyi chos nyid zhi ba yin pas /
NK079(dzu)003:2004: de ltar rig pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK079(dzu)003:2005: dngos po thams cad la khyab pas zhi bar 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:2006: zhes sgyu 'phrul dra ba las bshad do //
NK079(dzu)003:2007: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:2008: zhi ba'i gtor ma'i le'u ste sum cu bdun pa'o ////da ni zhi ba'i sbyor ba'i las bshad de /
NK079(dzu)003:2009: lha mo rnams kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK079(dzu)003:2010: lha'i grub pa bsgoms par bya //
NK079(dzu)003:2011: byin rlabs thams cad zhi bsgoms nas //
NK079(dzu)003:2012: lha rnams kun kyang zhi bar 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)003:2014: lha dang lha mo grub pa'i dkyil 'khor las /
NK079(dzu)003:2015: thams cad zhi bar bsgoms nas /
NK079(dzu)003:2016: lha nyid kyang zhi ba yin na //
NK079(dzu)003:2019: gzhan du na chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes lha mo'i rang bzhin lta bu yang /
NK079(dzu)003:2020: yongs kyis zhi ba yin la /
NK079(dzu)003:2021: de ltar rig pa'i ye shes lha'i rang bzhin lta bu yang /
NK079(dzu)003:2022: rang bzhin gyis zhi ba yin te //
NK079(dzu)003:2023: de'i byin rlabs kyis thams cad du khyab pa yang /
NK079(dzu)003:2024: rang bzhin gyis zhi ba yin pas //
NK079(dzu)003:2026: zhes rdo rje bkod pa'i tan tra las 'byung ngo //
NK079(dzu)003:2027: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo 'phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:2028: zhi ba sbyor ba'i le'u ste sum cu rtsa brgyad pa'o ////da ni las bsdu ba bshad de //
NK079(dzu)003:2029: mtshan nyid med pa'i phyag rgya dang //
NK079(dzu)003:2030: de las dngos 'byung phyag rgya rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:2031: nges pa med par dpa' bos bshad //
NK079(dzu)003:2032: mkhas pas ci dga' sgyur na 'grub //
NK079(dzu)003:2034: gong du bshad pa thams cad mtshan nyid med pa'i phyag rgya ste /
NK079(dzu)003:2035: chos kyi sku la dngos por snang ba dang //
NK079(dzu)003:2036: mtshan mar bsgoms pa thams cad 'byung bas /
NK079(dzu)003:2038: chos kyi sku ma nor bar rig na /
NK079(dzu)003:2040: phyag rgya dang mtshan ma thams cad ji ltar bde ba dang /
NK079(dzu)003:2044: be ro tsa na nyid kyis bshad do //
NK079(dzu)003:2045: tan tra thabs kyi zhags pa dang //
NK079(dzu)003:2047: sgyu 'phrul dra ba la sogs te //
NK079(dzu)003:2048: tan tra du ma sde lnga las bshad do //
NK079(dzu)003:2049: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo 'phreng ba las /
NK079(dzu)003:2050: lus btus pa'i le'u ste sum cu dgu pa'o ////da ni las drag po'i phan yon bshad de //
NK079(dzu)003:2053: rgyas pas gzi brjid rnam par 'phel //
NK079(dzu)003:2054: zhi bas bde ba'i mchog kyang 'grub //
NK079(dzu)003:2056: drag po spyad pas ni 'di dang gzhan du lha
NK079(dzu)003:2057: dang bdud la sogs thams cad thul bar 'gyur ro
NK079(dzu)003:2058: // dbang gi las byas pas ni 'di dang gzhan du longs spyod mchog dang /
NK079(dzu)003:2060: rgyas pa'i las byas pas ni 'di dang gzhan du dpal dang gzi brjid 'phel bar 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:2061: zhi ba'i las spyad pas ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2062: 'di dang gzhan du bde ba'i mchog thob par 'gyur ro //
NK079(dzu)003:2063: 'di dag ni bsod nams kyi tshogs chen po yin te /
NK079(dzu)003:2064: mtshan nyid med pa las mi gnas par rig pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2065: ye shes kyi tshogs chen po yin pas /
NK079(dzu)003:2066: phyag rgya chen po'i don rig par byas la //
NK079(dzu)003:2067: las rnam bzhi rgyun du brtsam par bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:2068: zhes ma ha yo ga'i tan tra du ma las bshad do //
NK079(dzu)003:2069: gang las 'byung ba'i lha cig la bsgrub na yang /
NK079(dzu)003:2070: dngos grub grangs med pa de bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
NK079(dzu)003:2071: zhes kyang du ma las bshad do //
NK079(dzu)003:2072: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo 'phreng ba las /
NK079(dzu)003:2073: las bsgrub phan yon gyi le'u ste bzhi bcu pa'o ////dkyil 'khor 'di'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2074: dbang chen bsdus pa'i dkyil 'khor te //
NK079(dzu)003:2075: de la dkyil 'khor gzhi zlum po bya ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2076: chos kyi dbyings spros pa med pa'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:2077: 'khor lo'i rtsibs zur can du bya zhing /
NK079(dzu)003:2078: gzhi zlum po'i nang na gnas pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2079: chos kyi dbyings spros pa med bzhin du byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK079(dzu)003:2080: lha dang lha mo dang khro bo dang khro mo dang /
NK079(dzu)003:2081: pho nya la sogs pa dang /
NK079(dzu)003:2083: rnam gcig tu na chos kyi dbyings rnam par rtog pa med bzhin du /
NK079(dzu)003:2084: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes ci yang mkhyen pa lhun gyis grub pa la bya ba'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:2085: mtha' gru bzhir bya ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2086: phyogs bcu'i snod dang bcud kyi 'jig rten thams cad la dbang sgyur bas /
NK079(dzu)003:2087: bde ba chen po rgyas pa'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:2088: dkyil nas lha mo kha phyir lta ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2089: lha mo ni dbyings nyid nye ba'i byin rlabs te /
NK079(dzu)003:2090: sems dpa' dbyings nyid nye ba'i mthong ba'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:2091: sems dpa' lnga nang du lta ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2092: chos nyid nye ba la lta ba'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:2093: sems dpa' gzhan phyir lta ba ni //
NK079(dzu)003:2095: sa rdo lta bur bems po ni ma yin gyi /
NK079(dzu)003:2096: mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang ldan zhing //
NK079(dzu)003:2097: sems dpa' nyid kyang dbyings las mi zhan pa'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:2098: sems ma gzhan nang du lta ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2099: mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang dngos po la sogs pa
NK079(dzu)003:2100: thams cad du rnam par rtog pa ma yin gyi
NK079(dzu)003:2102: dbyings nyid mkhyen pa'i ye shes las mi zhan pa'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:2103: rnam cig tu na sems dpa' phyir lta ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2104: snod dang bcud kyi 'jig rten thams cad dbang du sgyur ba'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:2105: sems ma nang du lta ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2106: snod dang bcud kyi 'jig rten thams cad dbang du 'dus pa'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:2107: sems dpa' dang sems ma phyi nang du gcig la gcig gzigs pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2108: mnyes par byed pa'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:2109: khro bo dang khro mo'i ril phyir blta ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2110: phyi'i dngos po dang rgol ba la sogs pa 'joms shing 'dul ba'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:2111: de la dbyings ni dper na nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor lta bu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:2112: mkhyen pa'i ye shes ni nyi ma'i 'od snang gsal ba lta bu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:2113: de'i byin rlabs ni dro zhing tsha ba lta bu'o //
NK079(dzu)003:2114: phyi'i dngos po dang rgol ba la sogs pa 'joms
NK079(dzu)003:2115: shing 'dul ba ni rtsi shing skyes shing 'tshig pa
NK079(dzu)003:2116: lta bu'o // lha mo dang sems dpa' ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2117: chos kyi dbyings nyid rig pa'i don dbyings la snang ba'o //
NK079(dzu)003:2119: dbyings la snang ba'i don mthong ba'o //
NK079(dzu)003:2120: dbyings nyid la snang ba dang mthong ba'i byin rlabs ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2121: rang bzhin gyis dngos po dang /
NK079(dzu)003:2122: rgol ba'i rang bzhin lhan gyis 'joms shing /
NK079(dzu)003:2123: dbyings su sbyor bar 'dul ba ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2124: khro bo dang khro mo las rnam bzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis mdzad cing /
NK079(dzu)003:2125: thugs rjes rten skyong ba'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:2126: 'jig rten skyong ba la sogs pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2127: byin rlabs pho nya lta bu gnas pa yin /
NK079(dzu)003:2128: rnam gcig tu 'jig rten gyi lha mthu bo che
NK079(dzu)003:2129: dang mthu mo che 'khor du 'dus pa'i rtags so
NK079(dzu)003:2130: // bkra shis brgyad ni thams cad la dbang bsgyur zhing 'khor ba la longs spyod kyang /
NK079(dzu)003:2131: nyon mongs pas 'ching bar mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK079(dzu)003:2132: mya ngan las 'das pa la spyad kyang nyan thos zhi ba phyogs gcig par mi 'gyur te /
NK079(dzu)003:2133: gang gis kyang zil gyis mi gnon pas bkra shis so //
NK079(dzu)003:2134: de la'ang dpal gyi be'u ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2135: mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang ldan pas bkra shis so //
NK079(dzu)003:2136: 'khor lo ni thabs la dbang bsgyur ba dang //
NK079(dzu)003:2137: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bkra shis so //
NK079(dzu)003:2139: zad mi shes pa'i gter dang ldan pas bkra shis so //
NK079(dzu)003:2141: 'khor bas ma zin pa'i bkra shis so //
NK079(dzu)003:2143: nyon mongs pas mi gdugs pas bkra shis so //
NK079(dzu)003:2145: ro mchog dang ldan pas bkra shis so //
NK079(dzu)003:2147: rgol ba thams cad skong bas sgra sgrogs pa'i bkra shis so //
NK079(dzu)003:2149: lam rgyud lnga'i sems can dang /
NK079(dzu)003:2150: ngan song kun las sgrol ba'i thugs rjes thabs mkhas pa'i bkra shis so //
NK079(dzu)003:2151: gling bzhi ni rigs lnga'i byin rlabs yin pa'am /
NK079(dzu)003:2153: de bzhin gshegs pa rang bzhin yod par bstan pa'am /
NK079(dzu)003:2154: thugs rje de dag gi don mdzad pa'i tha tshig go //
NK079(dzu)003:2155: rnam pa gcig tu thams cad dbang du 'dus pa'i don to //
NK079(dzu)003:2156: de la gtso bo dang gtso mo 'khor lnga lnga dang bcas pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2158: sems dpa' dang sems ma nyi shu ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2159: kun la bu gcig bzhin no //
NK079(dzu)003:2160: de ltar byams pa'i shugs kyis /
NK079(dzu)003:2161: khro bo dang khro mo 'khor dang bcas pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2162: phyi nang thams cad kyi dngos po la /
NK079(dzu)003:2163: rngon pas ri dwags mthong ba bzhin du ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2164: de ltar zhe sdang gi shugs kyis thams cad dbyings nyid la sbyor ro //
NK079(dzu)003:2165: 'byor na 'khor ba'i chos la spyad kyang /
NK079(dzu)003:2167: nyon mongs pas 'ching bar mi 'gyur bas /
NK079(dzu)003:2168: de ltar grub pa ni 'dod chags so //
NK079(dzu)003:2169: chos kyi dbyings ngang gis gsang pas phrag dog go //
NK079(dzu)003:2170: chos nyid spros pa med pas gti mug go //
NK079(dzu)003:2171: chos nyid de lta bus khams gsum las rgyal bas nga rgyal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:2172: de la gtso bo'i 'khor lnga'i byin rlabs ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2174: nye ba ni dbus nas mdun dang /
NK079(dzu)003:2175: thod ka yan chad rgyab mjug do yan chad do //
NK079(dzu)003:2176: mi 'khrugs pa'i 'khor lnga'i byin rlabs ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2177: phyag g.yas dang rtsibs log g.yas so //
NK079(dzu)003:2178: rin chen 'byung gnas kyi 'khor lnga'i byin rlabs ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2179: phyag g.yon dang rtsibs logs g.yon no //
NK079(dzu)003:2180: 'od dpag med kyi 'khor lnga'i byin rlabs ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2181: zhabs g.yon nas rked pa man chad do //
NK079(dzu)003:2182: don yod grub pa'i byin rlabs ni zhabs g.yas pa nas /
NK079(dzu)003:2183: rked pa g.yas man chad do //
NK079(dzu)003:2184: khro bo dang khro mo thams cad ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2185: rigs so so'i byin brlabs bzhin no //
NK079(dzu)003:2186: de ltar 'khor lnga po gcig la yang lnga lngar 'gyur te /
NK079(dzu)003:2187: sra ba'i bya ba byed pa thams cad ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2189: dro ba'i bya ba byed pa thams cad ni //
NK079(dzu)003:2191: gsher ba'i bya ba byed pa thams cad ni //
NK079(dzu)003:2193: bskyod pa'i bya ba byed pa thams cad ni //
NK079(dzu)003:2196: dngos su gzhag pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs so //
NK079(dzu)003:2199: dbus su 'gyur ba thams cad de //
NK079(dzu)003:2200: sra ba'i rang bzhin med pa ni //
NK079(dzu)003:2203: dro ba'i rang bzhin med pa ni //
NK079(dzu)003:2206: gsher ba'i rang bzhin med pa ni //
NK079(dzu)003:2207: gos dkar mo 'khor lnga'i byin rlabs so //
NK079(dzu)003:2208: bskyed pa'i rang bzhin med pa ni //
NK079(dzu)003:2209: sgrol ma'i 'khor lnga'i byin rlabs so //
NK079(dzu)003:2210: don du bya ba byed nus pa ni sems dpa' 'o //
NK079(dzu)003:2211: de bzhin du rang bzhin med pa ni /
NK079(dzu)003:2213: de ltar rig pa'i ni khro bo dang khro mo'o //
NK079(dzu)003:2214: de la bsdu zhing spro ba yang thams cad de ltar bya'o //
NK079(dzu)003:2215: phyi nang gi chos thams cad kyang de ltar rtag go //
NK079(dzu)003:2216: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo 'phreng las /
NK079(dzu)003:2217: dbang chen bsdus pa dkyil 'khor gyi le'u ste bzhi
NK079(dzu)003:2218: bcu rtsa gcig pa'o ////de skad ces dpal rnam par
NK079(dzu)003:2219: snang mdzad kyis bka' stsal ba /
NK079(dzu)003:2220: rdo rje gzhon nu'i sde 'bum phrag du ma yi rang ste /
NK079(dzu)003:2222: h'u bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba yi //
NK079(dzu)003:2224: khro bo khro mo rnams bzhugs pa //
NK079(dzu)003:2225: sku ni cir yang ma nges 'gyur ba'i gzugs //
NK079(dzu)003:2226: h'u dbu skra khams nag ral pa can //
NK079(dzu)003:2228: mi mnyam khro gnyer sdang dmigs ni //
NK079(dzu)003:2229: log pa lta ba 'dul ba'i mtshan //
NK079(dzu)003:2230: h'u mche ba zang yag gtsigs pas ni //
NK079(dzu)003:2231: skye shi rtsad nas gcod pa'i tshul //
NK079(dzu)003:2232: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs ni //
NK079(dzu)003:2233: phyag cha sna tshogs cir yang snang //
NK079(dzu)003:2234: h'u thugs rje'i byin rlabs sprin ltar gtibs //
NK079(dzu)003:2236: rngam pa'i sgra skad 'brug ltar sgrogs //
NK079(dzu)003:2237: sprul pa'i thogs chen char bzhin 'bebs //
NK079(dzu)003:2238: h'u sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni //
NK079(dzu)003:2239: klan ka chen po bdud la tshol //
NK079(dzu)003:2240: rgyal ka chen po bgegs la mdzad //
NK079(dzu)003:2241: bdud dpung ma lus 'dul ba dang //
NK079(dzu)003:2242: bgegs rnams thams cad 'joms mdzad cing //
NK079(dzu)003:2243: dam tshig can la dngos grub stsol //
NK079(dzu)003:2244: h'u thugs rje chen po byin rlabs kyis //
NK079(dzu)003:2245: bdag la byin gyis brlabs mdzad cing //
NK079(dzu)003:2246: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:2247: grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK079(dzu)003:2248: h'u 'khyil zhing rgyan yang 'khyil ba la //
NK079(dzu)003:2249: sems kyi chos la sku mi mnga' //sgra las 'das pa'i sbyor ba ste //
NK079(dzu)003:2250: bsam dang bral ba'i ye shes lags //
NK079(dzu)003:2251: h'u srid gsum 'joms pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:2252: mnyam nyid ngang gis khros la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:2253: khro bas longs spyod mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:2254: rdo rje 'du 'phro mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:2256: nyid kyi thugs kar zhugs nas mi snang bar gyur to //
NK079(dzu)003:2257: mnyam las spros te 'byung ba'i las //
NK079(dzu)003:2258: skyes bu gang zhig rig pa des //
NK079(dzu)003:2259: gang zhig ji skad brjod pa'i sgra /
NK079(dzu)003:2260: thams cad tan tra zhes pa ni //
NK079(dzu)003:2261: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK079(dzu)003:2262: mgon po bdag nyid chen po yis //
NK079(dzu)003:2263: rdo rje 'khor lo bskor ba na //
NK079(dzu)003:2264: sngags kyi dbang po bkram pas gsungs //
NK079(dzu)003:2265: de las brten te mgon po yis //
NK079(dzu)003:2266: sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:2267: rnal 'byor bsgrub pa rtogs bya'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)003:2268: ma nor tsam du bshad pa yin //
NK079(dzu)003:2269: dngos grub mchog brnyes ya mtshan chen po yis //
NK079(dzu)003:2270: 'jig rten ma gyur pad+ma rgyal po las //
NK079(dzu)003:2271: de bzhin gshegs pa'i man ngag gsang chen rnams //
NK079(dzu)003:2272: klong nas bkrol mdzad de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK079(dzu)003:2273: 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo'i 'phreng ba las /
NK079(dzu)003:2274: rtog pa'i rgyal po don bsdus pa'i le'u ste bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis pa'o ///
NK079(dzu)003:2276: / 'phags pa thabs kyi zhags pa pad+mo'i 'phreng gi 'grel
NK079(dzu)003:2277: pa rdzogs so ////bkra shis ////rgya nag pe cin bstan
